name: nidoran-m
pokedex_entry: Stiffens its ears to sense danger. The larger its horns, the more powerful its secreted venom.

name: nidorino
pokedex_entry: An aggressive POKéMON that is quick to attack. The horn on its head secretes a powerful venom.

name: nidoking
pokedex_entry: It uses its powerful tail in battle to smash, constrict, then break the prey's bones.

name: clefairy
pokedex_entry: Its magical and cute appeal has many admirers. It is rare and found only in certain areas.

name: clefable
pokedex_entry: A timid fairy POKéMON that is rarely seen. It will run and hide the moment it senses people.

name: vulpix
pokedex_entry: At the time of birth, it has just one tail. The tail splits from its tip as it grows older.

forms.name: alolan-vulpix
forms.pokedex_entry: At the time of birth, it has just one tail. The tail splits from its tip as it grows older.

forms.name: alolan-ninetales
forms.pokedex_entry: Very smart and very vengeful. Grabbing one of its many tails could result in a 1000-year curse.

name: jigglypuff
pokedex_entry: When its huge eyes light up, it sings a mysteriously soothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep.

name: wigglytuff
pokedex_entry: The body is soft and rubbery. When angered, it will suck in air and inflate itself to an enormous size.

name: zubat
pokedex_entry: Forms colonies in perpetually dark places. Uses ultrasonic waves to identify and approach targets.

name: golbat
pokedex_entry: Once it strikes, it will not stop draining energy from the victim even if it gets too heavy to fly.

name: oddish
pokedex_entry: During the day, it keeps its face buried in the ground. At night, it wanders around sowing its seeds.

name: gloom
pokedex_entry: The fluid that oozes from its mouth isn't drool. It is a nectar that is used to attract prey.

name: vileplume
pokedex_entry: It has the world’s largest petals. With every step, the petals shake out heavy clouds of toxic pollen.

name: paras
pokedex_entry: Burrows to suck tree roots. The mushrooms on its back grow by draw­ ing nutrients from the bug host.

name: parasect
pokedex_entry: A host-parasite pair in which the parasite mushroom has taken over the host bug. Prefers damp places.

name: venonat
pokedex_entry: Lives in the shadows of tall trees where it eats insects. It is attracted by light at night.

name: venomoth
pokedex_entry: The dustlike scales covering its wings are color-coded to indicate the kinds of poison it has.

forms.name: alolan-diglett

name: mankey
pokedex_entry: Extremely quick to anger. It could be docile one moment then thrashing away the next instant.

name: primeape
pokedex_entry: Always furious and tenacious to boot. It will not abandon chasing its quarry until it is caught.

name: poliwhirl
pokedex_entry: Capable of living in or out of water. When out of water, it sweats to keep its body slimy.

name: poliwrath
pokedex_entry: An adept swimmer at both the front crawl and breast stroke. Easily overtakes the best human swimmers.

name: abra
pokedex_entry: Using its ability to read minds, it will identify impending danger and TELEPORT to safety.

name: kadabra
pokedex_entry: It emits special alpha waves from its body that induce headaches just by being close by.

name: alakazam
pokedex_entry: Its brain can out­ perform a super­ computer. Its intelligence quotient is said to be 5,000.

forms.name: alakazam-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: Its brain can out­ perform a super­ computer. Its intelligence quotient is said to be 5,000.

name: machop

name: machoke
pokedex_entry: Its muscular body is so powerful, it must wear a power save belt to be able to regulate its motions.

name: machamp
pokedex_entry: Using its heavy muscles, it throws powerful punches that can send the victim clear over the horizon.

forms.name: machamp-gmax
forms.pokedex_entry: Using its heavy muscles, it throws powerful punches that can send the victim clear over the horizon.

name: bellsprout
pokedex_entry: A carnivorous POKéMON that traps and eats bugs. It uses its root feet to soak up needed moisture.

name: weepinbell
pokedex_entry: It spits out POISONPOWDER to immobilize the enemy and then finishes it with a spray of ACID.

name: victreebel
pokedex_entry: Said to live in huge colonies deep in jungles, although no one has ever returned from there.

name: tentacool
pokedex_entry: Drifts in shallow seas. Anglers who hook them by accident are often punished by its stinging acid.

name: tentacruel
pokedex_entry: The tentacles are normally kept short. On hunts, they are extended to ensnare and immobilize prey.

name: dodrio

name: seel
pokedex_entry: The protruding horn on its head is very hard. It is used for bashing through thick ice.

name: dewgong

name: cloyster
pokedex_entry: When attacked, it launches its horns in quick volleys. Its innards have never been seen.

name: gastly
pokedex_entry: Almost invisible, this gaseous POKéMON cloaks the target and puts it to sleep without notice.

name: haunter
pokedex_entry: Because of its ability to slip through block walls, it is said to be from an­ other dimension.

name: drowzee

name: hypno
pokedex_entry: When it locks eyes with an enemy, it will use a mix of PSI moves such as HYPNOSIS and CONFUSION.

name: krabby
pokedex_entry: Its pincers are not only powerful weapons, they are used for balance when walking sideways.

name: hitmonchan
pokedex_entry: While apparently doing nothing, it fires punches in lightning fast volleys that are impossible to see.

name: lickitung
pokedex_entry: Its tongue can be extended like a chameleon's. It leaves a tingling sensation when it licks enemies.

name: koffing

forms.name: galarian-weezing

name: rhydon
pokedex_entry: Protected by an armor-like hide, it is capable of living in molten lava of 3,600 degrees.

name: chansey
pokedex_entry: A rare and elusive POKéMON that is said to bring happiness to those who manage to get it.

name: tangela
pokedex_entry: The whole body is swathed with wide vines that are similar to sea­ weed. Its vines shake as it walks.

name: kangaskhan

forms.name: kangaskhan-mega

name: seadra

name: goldeen
pokedex_entry: Its tail fin billows like an elegant ballroom dress, giving it the nickname of the Water Queen.

name: seaking
pokedex_entry: In the autumn spawning season, they can be seen swimming powerfully up rivers and creeks.

name: staryu

name: starmie

name: electabuzz

name: magmar

forms.pokedex_entry: Its genetic code is irregular. It may mutate if it is exposed to radiation from element STONEs.

name: vaporeon
pokedex_entry: Lives close to water. Its long tail is ridged with a fin which is often mistaken for a mermaid's.

name: jolteon
pokedex_entry: It accumulates negative ions in the atmosphere to blast out 10000- volt lightning bolts.

name: flareon
pokedex_entry: When storing thermal energy in its body, its temperature could soar to over 1600 degrees.

name: porygon
pokedex_entry: A POKéMON that consists entirely of programming code. Capable of moving freely in cyberspace.

name: omanyte
pokedex_entry: Although long extinct, in rare cases, it can be genetically resurrected from fossils.

name: omastar
pokedex_entry: A prehistoric POKéMON that died out when its heavy shell made it impossible to catch prey.

name: kabuto
pokedex_entry: A POKéMON that was resurrected from a fossil found in what was once the ocean floor eons ago.

name: kabutops
pokedex_entry: Its sleek shape is perfect for swim­ ming. It slashes prey with its claws and drains the body fluids.

name: aerodactyl
pokedex_entry: A Pokémon that roamed the skies in the dinosaur era. Its teeth are like saw blades.

forms.name: aerodactyl-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: A Pokémon that roamed the skies in the dinosaur era. Its teeth are like saw blades.

name: snorlax
pokedex_entry: Very lazy. Just eats and sleeps. As its rotund bulk builds, it becomes steadily more slothful.

forms.name: snorlax-gmax
forms.pokedex_entry: Very lazy. Just eats and sleeps. As its rotund bulk builds, it becomes steadily more slothful.

name: articuno
pokedex_entry: A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appear to doomed people who are lost in icy mountains.

forms.name: galarian-articuno
forms.pokedex_entry: A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appear to doomed people who are lost in icy mountains.

name: zapdos
pokedex_entry: A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appear from clouds while dropping enormous lightning bolts.

forms.name: galarian-zapdos
forms.pokedex_entry: A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appear from clouds while dropping enormous lightning bolts.

name: moltres
pokedex_entry: Known as the legendary bird of fire. Every flap of its wings creates a dazzling flash of flames.

forms.name: galarian-moltres
forms.pokedex_entry: Known as the legendary bird of fire. Every flap of its wings creates a dazzling flash of flames.

name: dratini
pokedex_entry: Long considered a mythical POKéMON until recently when a small colony was found living underwater.

name: dragonair
pokedex_entry: A mystical POKéMON that exudes a gentle aura. Has the ability to change climate conditions.

name: dragonite
pokedex_entry: An extremely rarely seen marine POKéMON. Its intelligence is said to match that of humans.

name: mewtwo
pokedex_entry: It was created by a scientist after years of horrific gene splicing and DNA engineering experiments.

forms.name: mewtwo-mega-x
forms.pokedex_entry: It was created by a scientist after years of horrific gene splicing and DNA engineering experiments.

forms.name: mewtwo-mega-y
forms.pokedex_entry: It was created by a scientist after years of horrific gene splicing and DNA engineering experiments.

name: mew
pokedex_entry: So rare that it is still said to be a mirage by many experts. Only a few people have seen it worldwide.

name: chikorita
pokedex_entry: A sweet aroma gently wafts from the leaf on its head. It is docile and loves to soak up the sun's rays.

name: bayleef
pokedex_entry: The scent of spices comes from around its neck. Somehow, sniffing it makes you want to fight.

name: meganium
pokedex_entry: The aroma that rises from its petals contains a substance that calms aggressive feelings.

name: cyndaquil
pokedex_entry: It has a timid nature. If it is startled, the flames on its back burn more vigorously.

name: quilava
pokedex_entry: Be careful if it turns its back during battle. It means that it will attack with the fire on its back.

name: typhlosion
pokedex_entry: If its rage peaks, it becomes so hot that anything that touches it will instantly go up in flames.

forms.name: hisuian-typhlosion
forms.pokedex_entry: If its rage peaks, it becomes so hot that anything that touches it will instantly go up in flames.

name: totodile
pokedex_entry: Its well-developed jaws are powerful and capable of crushing anything. Even its trainer must be careful.

name: croconaw
pokedex_entry: If it loses a fang, a new one grows back in its place. There are always 48 fangs lining its mouth.

name: feraligatr
pokedex_entry: When it bites with its massive and powerful jaws, it shakes its head and savagely tears its victim up.

name: sentret
pokedex_entry: A very cautious POKéMON, it raises itself up using its tail to get a better view of its surroundings.

name: furret
pokedex_entry: It makes a nest to suit its long and skinny body. The nest is impossible for other POKéMON to enter.

name: hoothoot
pokedex_entry: It always stands on one foot. It changes feet so fast, the movement can rarely be seen.

name: noctowl
pokedex_entry: Its eyes are specially adapted. They concentrate even faint light and enable it to see in the dark.

name: ledyba
pokedex_entry: It is very timid. It will be afraid to move if it is alone. But it will be active if it is in a group.

name: ledian
pokedex_entry: When the stars flicker in the night sky, it flutters about, scattering a glowing powder.

name: spinarak
pokedex_entry: It lies still in the same pose for days in its web, waiting for its unsuspecting prey to wander close.

name: ariados
pokedex_entry: It spins string not only from its rear but also from its mouth. It is hard to tell which end is which.

name: crobat
pokedex_entry: It flies so si­ lently through the dark on its four wings that it may not be noticed even when nearby.

name: chinchou
pokedex_entry: Chinchou blink their shining antennae at one another to claim their respective turf.

name: lanturn
pokedex_entry: The light it emits is so bright that it can illuminate the sea's surface from a depth of over three miles.

name: pichu
pokedex_entry: It is not yet skilled at storing electricity. It may send out a jolt if amused or startled.

name: cleffa
pokedex_entry: Because of its unusual, star-like silhouette, people believe that it came here on a meteor.

name: igglybuff
pokedex_entry: It has a very soft body. If it starts to roll, it will bounce all over and be impossible to stop.

name: togepi
pokedex_entry: The shell seems to be filled with joy. It is said that it will share good luck when treated kindly.

name: togetic
pokedex_entry: They say that it will appear before kindhearted, car­ ing people and shower them with happiness.

name: natu
pokedex_entry: Because its wings aren't yet fully grown, it has to hop to get around. It is always star­ ing at something.

name: xatu
pokedex_entry: They say that it stays still and quiet because it is seeing both the past and future at the same time.

name: mareep
pokedex_entry: If static elec­ tricity builds in its body, its fleece doubles in volume. Touching it will shock you.

name: flaaffy
pokedex_entry: As a result of storing too much electricity, it developed patches where even downy wool won't grow.

name: ampharos
pokedex_entry: The tail's tip shines brightly and can be seen from far away. It acts as a beacon for lost people.

forms.name: ampharos-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: The tail's tip shines brightly and can be seen from far away. It acts as a beacon for lost people.

name: bellossom
pokedex_entry: Plentiful in the tropics. When it dances, its petals rub together and make a pleasant ringing sound.

name: marill
pokedex_entry: The tip of its tail, which con­ tains oil that is lighter than wa­ ter, lets it swim without drowning.

name: azumarill
pokedex_entry: It lives in water virtually all day long. Its body color and pattern act as camouflage that makes it tough for enemies to spot in water.

name: sudowoodo
pokedex_entry: Although it always pretends to be a tree, its composi­ tion appears to be closer to a rock than a plant.

name: politoed
pokedex_entry: If POLIWAG and POLIWHIRL hear its echoing cry, they respond by gather­ ing from far and wide.

name: hoppip
pokedex_entry: To keep from being blown away by the wind, they gather in clusters. They do enjoy gentle breezes, though.

name: skiploom
pokedex_entry: The bloom on top of its head opens and closes as the temperature fluc­ tuates up and down.

name: jumpluff
pokedex_entry: Once it catches the wind, it deft­ ly controls its cotton-puff spores to float, even around the world.

name: aipom
pokedex_entry: Its tail is so powerful that it can use it to grab a tree branch and hold itself up in the air.

name: sunkern
pokedex_entry: It may drop out of the sky suddenly. If attacked by a SPEAROW, it will violently shake its leaves.

name: sunflora
pokedex_entry: It converts sun­ light into energy. In the darkness after sunset, it closes its petals and becomes still.

name: yanma
pokedex_entry: If it flaps its wings really fast, it can generate shock waves that will shatter win­ dows in the area.

name: wooper
pokedex_entry: This POKéMON lives in cold water. It will leave the water to search for food when it gets cold outside.

forms.name: wooper-paldea
forms.pokedex_entry: This POKéMON lives in cold water. It will leave the water to search for food when it gets cold outside.

name: quagsire
pokedex_entry: This carefree POKéMON has an easy-going nature. While swimming, it always bumps into boat hulls.

name: espeon
pokedex_entry: It uses the fine hair that covers its body to sense air currents and predict its ene­ my's actions.

name: umbreon
pokedex_entry: When agitated, this POKéMON pro­ tects itself by spraying poisonous sweat from its pores.

name: murkrow
pokedex_entry: Feared and loathed by many, it is believed to bring misfortune to all those who see it at night.

name: slowking
pokedex_entry: It has incredible intellect and in­ tuition. Whatever the situation, it remains calm and collected.

forms.name: galarian-slowking
forms.pokedex_entry: It has incredible intellect and in­ tuition. Whatever the situation, it remains calm and collected.

name: misdreavus
pokedex_entry: It likes playing mischievous tricks such as screaming and wailing to startle people at night.

name: unown
pokedex_entry: Their shapes look like hieroglyphs on ancient tab­ lets. It is said that the two are somehow related.

name: wobbuffet
pokedex_entry: It hates light and shock. If attack­ ed, it inflates its body to pump up its counter­ strike.

name: girafarig
pokedex_entry: Its tail has a small brain of its own. Beware! If you get close, it may react to your scent and bite.

name: pineco
pokedex_entry: It likes to make its shell thicker by adding layers of tree bark. The additional weight doesn't bother it.

name: forretress
pokedex_entry: Its entire body is shielded by a steel-hard shell. What lurks inside the armor is a total mystery.

name: dunsparce
pokedex_entry: When spotted, this POKéMON escapes backward by furi­ ously boring into the ground with its tail.

name: gligar
pokedex_entry: It flies straight at its target's face then clamps down on the star­ tled victim to inject poison.

name: steelix
pokedex_entry: It is thought its body transformed as a result of iron accumulating internally from swallowing soil.

forms.name: steelix-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: It is thought its body transformed as a result of iron accumulating internally from swallowing soil.

name: snubbull
pokedex_entry: Although it looks frightening, it is actually kind and affectionate. It is very popular among women.

name: granbull
pokedex_entry: It is actually timid and easily spooked. If at­ tacked, it flails about to fend off its attacker.

name: qwilfish
pokedex_entry: To fire its poison spikes, it must inflate its body by drinking over 2.6 gallons of water all at once.

forms.name: hisuian-qwilfish
forms.pokedex_entry: To fire its poison spikes, it must inflate its body by drinking over 2.6 gallons of water all at once.

name: scizor
pokedex_entry: It has a steel-hard body. It intimidates foes by upraising its eye-patterned pincers.

forms.name: scizor-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: It has a steel-hard body. It intimidates foes by upraising its eye-patterned pincers.

name: shuckle
pokedex_entry: The BERRIES it stores in its vase-like shell decompose and become a gooey liquid.

name: heracross
pokedex_entry: It is usually docile, but if it is disturbed while sipping honey, it chases off the intruder with its horn.

forms.name: heracross-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: It is usually docile, but if it is disturbed while sipping honey, it chases off the intruder with its horn.

name: sneasel
pokedex_entry: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it sud­ denly extends the claws and startles its enemy.

forms.name: hisuian-sneasel
forms.pokedex_entry: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it sud­ denly extends the claws and startles its enemy.

name: teddiursa
pokedex_entry: If it finds honey, its crescent mark glows. It always licks its paws because they are soaked with honey.

name: ursaring
pokedex_entry: Although it is a good climber, it prefers to snap trees with its forelegs and eat fallen BERRIES.

name: slugma
pokedex_entry: It never sleeps. It has to keep moving because if it stopped, its magma body would cool and harden.

name: magcargo
pokedex_entry: The shell on its back is just skin that has cooled and hardened. It breaks easily with a slight touch.

name: swinub
pokedex_entry: It rubs its snout on the ground to find and dig up food. It sometimes discovers hot springs.

name: piloswine
pokedex_entry: Because the long hair all over its body obscures its sight, it just keeps charging repeatedly.

name: corsola
pokedex_entry: It continuously sheds and grows. The tip of its head is prized as a treasure for its beauty.

forms.name: galarian-corsola
forms.pokedex_entry: It continuously sheds and grows. The tip of its head is prized as a treasure for its beauty.

name: remoraid
pokedex_entry: It has superb ac­ curacy. The water it shoots out can strike even moving prey from more than 300 feet.

name: octillery
pokedex_entry: It traps enemies with its suction- cupped tentacles then smashes them with its rock-hard head.

name: delibird
pokedex_entry: It carries food all day long. There are tales about lost people who were saved by the food it had.

name: mantine
pokedex_entry: As it majestically swims, it doesn't care if REMORAID attach to it for scavenging its leftovers.

name: skarmory
pokedex_entry: Its sturdy wings look heavy, but they are actually hollow and light, allowing it to fly freely in the sky.

name: houndour
pokedex_entry: It uses different kinds of cries for communicating with others of its kind and for pursuing its prey.

name: houndoom
pokedex_entry: If you are burned by the flames it shoots from its mouth, the pain will never go away.

forms.name: houndoom-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: If you are burned by the flames it shoots from its mouth, the pain will never go away.

name: kingdra
pokedex_entry: It is said that it usually hides in underwater caves. It can create whirlpools by yawning.

name: phanpy
pokedex_entry: It swings its long snout around play­ fully, but because it is so strong, that can be dan­ gerous.

name: donphan
pokedex_entry: It has sharp, hard tusks and a rugged hide. Its TACKLE is strong enough to knock down a house.

name: porygon2
pokedex_entry: This upgraded version of PORYGON is designed for space exploration. It can't fly, though.

name: stantler
pokedex_entry: The curved antlers subtly change the flow of air to create a strange space where real­ ity is distorted.

name: smeargle
pokedex_entry: A special fluid oozes from the tip of its tail. It paints the fluid everywhere to mark its territory.

name: tyrogue
pokedex_entry: It is always bursting with en­ ergy. To make it­ self stronger, it keeps on fighting even if it loses.

name: hitmontop
pokedex_entry: If you become enchanted by its smooth, elegant, dance-like kicks, you may get drilled hard.

name: smoochum
pokedex_entry: Its lips are the most sensitive parts on its body. It always uses its lips first to examine things.

name: elekid
pokedex_entry: It rotates its arms to generate electricity, but it tires easily, so it charges up only a little bit.

name: magby
pokedex_entry: Each and every time it inhales and exhales, hot embers dribble out of its mouth and nostrils.

name: miltank
pokedex_entry: Its milk is packed with nutrition, making it the ultimate beverage for the sick or weary.

name: blissey
pokedex_entry: Anyone who takes even one bite of BLISSEY's egg be­ comes unfailingly caring and pleas­ ant to everyone.

name: raikou
pokedex_entry: The rain clouds it carries let it fire thunderbolts at will. They say that it descended with lightning.

name: entei
pokedex_entry: Volcanoes erupt when it barks. Un­ able to restrain its extreme power, it races headlong around the land.

name: suicune
pokedex_entry: It races around the world to purify fouled water. It dashes away with the north wind.

name: larvitar
pokedex_entry: It feeds on soil. After it has eaten a large mountain, it will fall asleep so it can grow.

name: pupitar
pokedex_entry: Its shell is as hard as sheet rock, and it is also very strong. Its THRASHING can topple a mountain.

name: tyranitar
pokedex_entry: Its body can't be harmed by any sort of attack, so it is very eager to make challenges against enemies.

forms.name: tyranitar-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: Its body can't be harmed by any sort of attack, so it is very eager to make challenges against enemies.

name: lugia
pokedex_entry: It is said that it quietly spends its time deep at the bottom of the sea because its powers are too strong.

name: ho-oh
pokedex_entry: Legends claim this POKéMON flies the world's skies con­ tinuously on its magnificent seven- colored wings.

name: celebi
pokedex_entry: This POKéMON wan­ ders across time. Grass and trees flourish in the forests in which it has appeared.

name: treecko
pokedex_entry: TREECKO has small hooks on the bottom of its feet that enable it to scale vertical walls. This POKéMON attacks by slamming foes with its thick tail.

name: grovyle
pokedex_entry: The leaves growing out of GROVYLE’s body are convenient for camouflaging it from enemies in the forest. This POKéMON is a master at climbing trees in jungles.

name: sceptile
pokedex_entry: The leaves growing on SCEPTILE’s body are very sharp edged. This POKéMON is very agile - it leaps all over the branches of trees and jumps on its foe from above or behind.

forms.name: sceptile-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: The leaves growing on SCEPTILE’s body are very sharp edged. This POKéMON is very agile - it leaps all over the branches of trees and jumps on its foe from above or behind.

name: torchic
pokedex_entry: TORCHIC sticks with its TRAINER, following behind with unsteady steps. This POKéMON breathes fire of over 1,800 degrees F, including fireballs that leave the foe scorched black.

name: combusken
pokedex_entry: COMBUSKEN toughens up its legs and thighs by running through fields and mountains. This POKéMON’s legs possess both speed and power, enabling it to dole out ten kicks in one second.

name: blaziken
pokedex_entry: In battle, BLAZIKEN blows out intense flames from its wrists and attacks foes courageously. The stronger the foe, the more intensely this POKéMON’s wrists burn.

forms.name: blaziken-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: In battle, BLAZIKEN blows out intense flames from its wrists and attacks foes courageously. The stronger the foe, the more intensely this POKéMON’s wrists burn.

name: mudkip
pokedex_entry: The fin on MUDKIP’s head acts as highly sensitive radar. Using this fin to sense movements of water and air, this POKéMON can determine what is taking place around it without using its eyes.

name: marshtomp
pokedex_entry: The surface of MARSHTOMP’s body is enveloped by a thin, sticky film that enables it to live on land. This POKéMON plays in mud on beaches when the ocean tide is low.

name: swampert
pokedex_entry: SWAMPERT is very strong. It has enough power to easily drag a boulder weighing more than a ton. This POKéMON also has powerful vision that lets it see even in murky water.

forms.name: swampert-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: SWAMPERT is very strong. It has enough power to easily drag a boulder weighing more than a ton. This POKéMON also has powerful vision that lets it see even in murky water.

name: poochyena
pokedex_entry: At first sight, POOCHYENA takes a bite at anything that moves. This POKéMON chases after prey until the victim becomes exhausted. However, it may turn tail if the prey strikes back.

name: mightyena
pokedex_entry: MIGHTYENA gives obvious signals when it is preparing to attack. It starts to growl deeply and then flattens its body. This POKéMON will bite savagely with its sharply pointed fangs.

name: zigzagoon
pokedex_entry: ZIGZAGOON restlessly wanders everywhere at all times. This POKéMON does so because it is very curious. It becomes interested in anything that it happens to see.

forms.name: galarian-zigzagoon
forms.pokedex_entry: ZIGZAGOON restlessly wanders everywhere at all times. This POKéMON does so because it is very curious. It becomes interested in anything that it happens to see.

name: linoone
pokedex_entry: LINOONE always runs full speed and only in straight lines. If facing an obstacle, it makes a right-angle turn to evade it. This POKéMON is very challenged by gently curving roads.

forms.name: galarian-linoone
forms.pokedex_entry: LINOONE always runs full speed and only in straight lines. If facing an obstacle, it makes a right-angle turn to evade it. This POKéMON is very challenged by gently curving roads.

name: wurmple
pokedex_entry: Using the spikes on its rear end,   WURMPLE peels the bark off trees and feeds on the sap that oozes out. This POKéMON’s feet are tipped with suction pads that allow it to cling to glass without slipping.

name: silcoon
pokedex_entry: SILCOON tethers itself to a tree branch using silk to keep from falling. There,  this POKéMON hangs quietly while it awaits evolution. It peers out of the silk cocoon through a small hole.

name: beautifly
pokedex_entry: BEAUTIFLY’s favorite food is the sweet pollen of flowers. If you want to see this POKéMON, just leave a potted flower by an open window. BEAUTIFLY is sure to come looking for pollen.

name: cascoon
pokedex_entry: CASCOON makes its protective cocoon by wrapping its body entirely with a fine silk from its mouth. Once the silk goes around its body, it hardens. This POKéMON prepares for its evolution inside the cocoon.

name: dustox
pokedex_entry: DUSTOX is instinctively drawn to light. Swarms of this POKéMON are attracted by the bright lights of cities, where they wreak havoc by stripping the leaves off roadside trees for food.

name: lotad
pokedex_entry: It searches about for clean water. If it does not drink water for too long, the leaf on its head wilts.

name: lombre
pokedex_entry: It lives at the water’s edge where it is sunny. It sleeps on a bed of water grass by day and becomes active at night.

name: ludicolo
pokedex_entry: LUDICOLO begins dancing as soon as it hears cheerful, festive music. This POKéMON is said to appear when it hears the singing of children on hiking outings.

name: seedot
pokedex_entry: SEEDOT attaches itself to a tree branch using the top of its head. It sucks moisture from the tree while hanging off the branch. The more water it drinks, the glossier this POKéMON’s body becomes.

name: nuzleaf
pokedex_entry: NUZLEAF live in densely overgrown forests. They occasionally venture out of the forest to startle people. This POKéMON dislikes having its long nose pinched.

name: shiftry
pokedex_entry: It lives quietly in the deep forest. It is said to create chilly winter winds with the fans it holds.

name: taillow
pokedex_entry: TAILLOW courageously stands its ground against foes, however strong they may be. This gutsy POKéMON will remain defiant even after a loss. On the other hand, it cries loudly if it becomes hungry.

name: swellow
pokedex_entry: SWELLOW flies high above our heads, making graceful arcs in the sky. This POKéMON dives at a steep angle as soon as it spots its prey. The hapless prey is tightly grasped by SWELLOW’s clawed feet, preventing escape.

name: wingull
pokedex_entry: WINGULL has the habit of carrying prey and valuables in its beak and hiding them in all sorts of locations. This POKéMON rides the winds and flies as if it were skating across the sky.

name: pelipper
pokedex_entry: It is a messenger of the skies, carrying small Pokémon and eggs to safety in its bill.

name: ralts
pokedex_entry: RALTS senses the emotions of people using the horns on its head. This POKéMON rarely appears before people. But when it does, it draws closer if it senses that the person has a positive disposition.

name: kirlia
pokedex_entry: It is said that a KIRLIA that is exposed to the positive emotions of its TRAINER grows beautiful. This POKéMON controls psychokinetic powers with its highly developed brain.

name: gardevoir
pokedex_entry: GARDEVOIR has the ability to read the future. If it senses impending danger to its TRAINER, this POKéMON is said to unleash its psychokinetic energy at full power.

forms.name: gardevoir-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: GARDEVOIR has the ability to read the future. If it senses impending danger to its TRAINER, this POKéMON is said to unleash its psychokinetic energy at full power.

name: surskit
pokedex_entry: From the tips of its feet, SURSKIT secretes an oil that enables it to walk on water as if it were skating. This POKéMON feeds on microscopic organisms in ponds and lakes.

name: masquerain
pokedex_entry: MASQUERAIN intimidates enemies with the eyelike patterns on its antennas. This POKéMON flaps its four wings to freely fly in any direction - even sideways and backwards - as if it were a helicopter.

name: shroomish
pokedex_entry: SHROOMISH live in damp soil in the dark depths of forests. They are often found keeping still under fallen leaves. This POKéMON feeds on compost that is made up of fallen, rotted leaves.

name: breloom
pokedex_entry: BRELOOM closes in on its foe with light and sprightly footwork, then throws punches with its stretchy arms. This POKéMON’s fighting technique puts boxers to shame.

name: slakoth
pokedex_entry: SLAKOTH lolls around for over twenty hours every day. Because it moves so little, it does not need much food. This POKéMON’s sole daily meal consists of just three leaves.

name: vigoroth
pokedex_entry: VIGOROTH is always itching and agitated to go on a wild rampage. It simply can’t tolerate sitting still for even a minute. This POKéMON’s stress level rises if it can’t be moving constantly.

name: slaking
pokedex_entry: SLAKING spends all day lying down and lolling about. It eats grass growing within its reach. If it eats all the grass it can reach, this POKéMON reluctantly moves to another spot.

name: nincada
pokedex_entry: NINCADA lives underground for many years in complete darkness. This POKéMON absorbs nutrients from the roots of trees. It stays motionless as it waits for evolution.

name: ninjask
pokedex_entry: NINJASK moves around at such a high speed that it cannot be seen, even while its crying can be clearly heard. For that reason, this POKéMON was long believed to be invisible.

name: shedinja
pokedex_entry: SHEDINJA’s hard body doesn’t move - not even a twitch. In fact, its body appears to be merely a hollow shell. It is believed that this POKéMON will steal the spirit of anyone peering into its hollow body from its back.

name: whismur
pokedex_entry: Normally, WHISMUR’s voice is very quiet - it is barely audible even if one is paying close attention. However, if this POKéMON senses danger, it starts crying at an earsplitting volume.

name: loudred
pokedex_entry: LOUDRED’s bellowing can completely decimate a wood-frame house. It uses its voice to punish its foes. This POKéMON’s round ears serve as loudspeakers.

name: exploud
pokedex_entry: EXPLOUD triggers earthquakes with the tremors it creates by bellowing. If this POKéMON violently inhales from the ports on its body, it’s a sign that it is preparing to let loose a huge bellow.

name: makuhita
pokedex_entry: MAKUHITA is tenacious - it will keep getting up and attacking its foe however many times it is knocked down. Every time it gets back up, this POKéMON stores more energy in its body for evolving.

name: hariyama
pokedex_entry: It has the habit of challenging others without hesitation to tests of strength. It’s been known to stand on train tracks and stop trains using forearm thrusts.

name: azurill
pokedex_entry: A Pokémon that lives by water. It moves quickly on land by bouncing on its big tail.

name: nosepass
pokedex_entry: NOSEPASS’s magnetic nose is always pointed to the north. If two of these POKéMON meet, they cannot turn their faces to each other when they are close because their magnetic noses repel one another.

name: skitty
pokedex_entry: SKITTY has the habit of becoming fascinated by moving objects and chasing them around. This POKéMON is known to chase after its own tail and become dizzy.

name: delcatty
pokedex_entry: DELCATTY prefers to live an unfettered existence in which it can do as it pleases at its own pace. Because this POKéMON eats and sleeps whenever it decides, its daily routines are completely random.

name: sableye
pokedex_entry: SABLEYE lead quiet lives deep inside caverns. They are feared, however, because these POKéMON are thought to steal the spirits of people when their eyes burn with a sinister glow in the darkness.

forms.name: sableye-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: SABLEYE lead quiet lives deep inside caverns. They are feared, however, because these POKéMON are thought to steal the spirits of people when their eyes burn with a sinister glow in the darkness.

name: mawile
pokedex_entry: MAWHILE’s huge jaws are actually steel horns that have been transformed. Its docile-looking face serves to lull its foe into letting down its guard. When the foe least expects it, MAWHILE chomps it with its gaping jaws.

forms.name: mawile-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: MAWHILE’s huge jaws are actually steel horns that have been transformed. Its docile-looking face serves to lull its foe into letting down its guard. When the foe least expects it, MAWHILE chomps it with its gaping jaws.

name: aron
pokedex_entry: This POKéMON has a body of steel. To make its body, ARON feeds on iron ore that it digs from mountains. Occasionally, it causes major trouble by eating bridges and rails.

name: lairon
pokedex_entry: LAIRON tempers its steel body by drinking highly nutritious mineral springwater until it is bloated. This POKéMON makes its nest close to springs of delicious water.

name: aggron
pokedex_entry: AGGRON claims an entire mountain as its own territory. It mercilessly beats up anything that violates its environment. This POKéMON vigilantly patrols its territory at all times.

forms.name: aggron-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: AGGRON claims an entire mountain as its own territory. It mercilessly beats up anything that violates its environment. This POKéMON vigilantly patrols its territory at all times.

name: meditite
pokedex_entry: MEDITITE undertakes rigorous mental training deep in the mountains. However, whenever it meditates, this POKéMON always loses its concentration and focus. As a result, its training never ends.

name: medicham
pokedex_entry: It is said that through meditation, MEDICHAM heightens energy inside its body and sharpens its sixth sense. This POKéMON hides its presence by merging itself with fields and mountains.

forms.name: medicham-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: It is said that through meditation, MEDICHAM heightens energy inside its body and sharpens its sixth sense. This POKéMON hides its presence by merging itself with fields and mountains.

name: electrike
pokedex_entry: ELECTRIKE stores electricity in its long body hair. This POKéMON stimulates its leg muscles with electric charges. These jolts of power give its legs explosive acceleration performance.

name: manectric
pokedex_entry: MANECTRIC is constantly discharging electricity from its mane. The sparks sometimes ignite forest fires. When it enters a battle, this POKéMON creates thunderclouds.

forms.name: manectric-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: MANECTRIC is constantly discharging electricity from its mane. The sparks sometimes ignite forest fires. When it enters a battle, this POKéMON creates thunderclouds.

name: plusle
pokedex_entry: PLUSLE always acts as a cheerleader for its partners. Whenever a teammate puts out a good effort in battle, this POKéMON shorts out its body to create the crackling noises of sparks to show its joy.

name: minun
pokedex_entry: MINUN is more concerned about cheering on its partners than its own safety. It shorts out the electricity in its body to create brilliant showers of sparks to cheer on its teammates.

name: volbeat
pokedex_entry: With the arrival of night, VOLBEAT emits light from its tail. It communicates with others by adjusting the intensity and flashing of its light. This POKéMON is attracted by the sweet aroma of ILLUMISE.

name: illumise
pokedex_entry: With its sweet aroma, it guides Volbeat to draw signs with light in the night sky.

name: roselia
pokedex_entry: ROSELIA shoots sharp thorns as projectiles at any opponent that tries to steal the flowers on its arms. The aroma of this POKéMON brings serenity to living things.

name: gulpin
pokedex_entry: Virtually all of GULPIN’s body is its stomach. As a result, it can swallow something its own size. This POKéMON’s stomach contains a special fluid that digests anything.

name: swalot
pokedex_entry: When SWALOT spots prey, it spurts out a hideously toxic fluid from its pores and sprays the target. Once the prey has weakened, this POKéMON gulps it down whole with its cavernous mouth.

name: carvanha
pokedex_entry: CARVANHA’s strongly developed jaws and its sharply pointed fangs pack the destructive power to rip out boat hulls. Many boats have been attacked and sunk by this POKéMON.

name: sharpedo
pokedex_entry: Nicknamed “the bully of the sea,” SHARPEDO is widely feared. Its cruel fangs grow back immediately if they snap off. Just one of these POKéMON can thoroughly tear apart a supertanker.

forms.name: sharpedo-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: Nicknamed “the bully of the sea,” SHARPEDO is widely feared. Its cruel fangs grow back immediately if they snap off. Just one of these POKéMON can thoroughly tear apart a supertanker.

name: wailmer
pokedex_entry: WAILMER’s nostrils are located above its eyes. This playful POKéMON loves to startle people by forcefully snorting out seawater it stores inside its body out of its nostrils.

name: wailord
pokedex_entry: WAILORD is the largest of all identified POKéMON up to now. This giant POKéMON swims languorously in the vast open sea, eating massive amounts of food at once with its enormous mouth.

name: numel
pokedex_entry: NUMEL is extremely dull witted - it doesn’t notice being hit. However, it can’t stand hunger for even a second. This POKéMON’s body is a seething cauldron of boiling magma.

name: camerupt
pokedex_entry: CAMERUPT has a volcano inside its body. Magma of 18,000 degrees F courses through its body. Occasionally, the humps on this POKéMON’s back erupt, spewing the superheated magma.

forms.name: camerupt-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: CAMERUPT has a volcano inside its body. Magma of 18,000 degrees F courses through its body. Occasionally, the humps on this POKéMON’s back erupt, spewing the superheated magma.

name: torkoal
pokedex_entry: You can tell how it’s feeling by the smoke spouting from its shell. Tremendous velocity is a sign of good health.

name: spoink
pokedex_entry: SPOINK bounces around on its tail. The shock of its bouncing makes its heart pump. As a result, this POKéMON cannot afford to stop bouncing - if it stops, its heart will stop.

name: grumpig
pokedex_entry: GRUMPIG uses the black pearls on its body to amplify its psychic power waves for gaining total control over its foe. When this POKéMON uses its special power, its snorting breath grows labored.

name: spinda
pokedex_entry: No two Spinda have the same pattern of spots. Its tottering step fouls the aim of foes.

name: trapinch
pokedex_entry: TRAPINCH’s nest is a sloped, bowl-like pit dug in sand. This POKéMON patiently waits for prey to tumble down the pit. Its giant jaws have enough strength to crush even boulders.

name: vibrava
pokedex_entry: To make prey faint, VIBRAVA generates ultrasonic waves by vigorously making its two wings vibrate. This POKéMON’s ultrasonic waves are so powerful, they can bring on headaches in people.

name: flygon
pokedex_entry: FLYGON is nicknamed “the elemental  spirit of the desert.” Because its flapping wings whip up a cloud of sand, this POKéMON is always enveloped in a sandstorm while flying.

name: cacnea
pokedex_entry: CACNEA lives in arid locations such as deserts. It releases a strong aroma from its flower to attract prey. When prey comes near, this POKéMON shoots sharp thorns from its body to bring the victim down.

name: cacturne
pokedex_entry: During the daytime, CACTURNE remains unmoving so that it does not lose any moisture to the harsh desert sun. This POKéMON becomes active at night when the temperature drops.

name: swablu
pokedex_entry: SWABLU has light and fluffy wings that are like cottony clouds. This POKéMON is not frightened of people. It lands on the heads of people and sits there like a cotton-fluff hat.

name: altaria
pokedex_entry: ALTARIA dances and wheels through the sky among billowing, cotton-like clouds. By singing melodies in its crystal-clear voice, this POKéMON makes its listeners experience dreamy wonderment.

forms.name: altaria-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: ALTARIA dances and wheels through the sky among billowing, cotton-like clouds. By singing melodies in its crystal-clear voice, this POKéMON makes its listeners experience dreamy wonderment.

name: zangoose
pokedex_entry: Memories of battling its arch-rival SEVIPER are etched into every cell of ZANGOOSE’s body. This POKéMON adroitly dodges attacks with incredible agility.

name: seviper
pokedex_entry: SEVIPER shares a generations-long feud with ZANGOOSE. The scars on its body are evidence of vicious battles. This POKéMON attacks using its sword- edged tail.

name: lunatone
pokedex_entry: LUNATONE was discovered at a location where a meteorite fell. As a result, some people theorize that this POKéMON came from space. However, no one has been able to prove this theory so far.

name: solrock
pokedex_entry: Solar energy is the source of its power, so it is strong during the daytime. When it spins, its body shines.

name: barboach
pokedex_entry: BARBOACH’s sensitive whiskers serve as a superb radar system. This POKéMON hides in mud, leaving only its two whiskers exposed while it waits for prey to come along.

name: whiscash
pokedex_entry: WHISCASH is extremely territorial. Just one of these POKéMON will claim a large pond as its exclusive territory. If a foe approaches it, it thrashes about and triggers a massive earthquake.

name: corphish
pokedex_entry: Its hardy vitality enables it to adapt to any environment. Its pincers will never release prey.

name: crawdaunt
pokedex_entry: CRAWDAUNT has an extremely violent nature that compels it to challenge other living things to battle. Other life-forms refuse to live in ponds inhabited by this POKéMON, making them desolate places.

name: baltoy
pokedex_entry: BALTOY moves while spinning around on its one foot. Primitive wall paintings depicting this POKéMON living among people were discovered in some ancient ruins.

name: claydol
pokedex_entry: CLAYDOL are said to be dolls of mud made by primitive humans and brought to life by exposure to a mysterious ray. This POKéMON moves about while levitating.

name: lileep
pokedex_entry: LILEEP became extinct approximately a hundred million years ago. This ancient POKéMON attaches itself to a rock on the seafloor and catches approaching prey using tentacles  shaped like flower petals.

name: cradily
pokedex_entry: CRADILY roams around the ocean floor in search of food. This POKéMON freely extends its tree trunk-like neck and captures unwary prey using its eight tentacles.

name: anorith
pokedex_entry: ANORITH was regenerated from a prehistoric fossil. This primitive POKéMON once lived in warm seas. It grips its prey firmly between its two large claws.

name: armaldo
pokedex_entry: ARMALDO’s tough armor makes all attacks bounce off. This POKéMON’s two enormous claws can be freely extended or contracted. They have the power to punch right through a steel slab.

name: feebas
pokedex_entry: FEEBAS’s fins are ragged and tattered from the start of its life. Because of its shoddy appearance, this POKéMON is largely ignored. It is capable of living in both the sea and in rivers.

name: milotic
pokedex_entry: Its lovely scales are described as rainbow colored. They change color depending on the viewing angle.

name: castform
pokedex_entry: CASTFORM’s appearance changes with the weather. This POKéMON gained the ability to use the vast power of nature to protect its tiny body.

forms.name: castform-sunny
forms.pokedex_entry: CASTFORM’s appearance changes with the weather. This POKéMON gained the ability to use the vast power of nature to protect its tiny body.

forms.name: castform-rainy
forms.pokedex_entry: CASTFORM’s appearance changes with the weather. This POKéMON gained the ability to use the vast power of nature to protect its tiny body.

forms.name: castform-snowy
forms.pokedex_entry: CASTFORM’s appearance changes with the weather. This POKéMON gained the ability to use the vast power of nature to protect its tiny body.

name: kecleon
pokedex_entry: It changes body color to blend in with its surroundings. It also changes color if it is happy or sad.

name: shuppet
pokedex_entry: SHUPPET is attracted by feelings of jealousy and vindictiveness. If someone develops strong feelings of vengeance, this POKéMON will appear in a swarm and line up beneath the eaves of that person’s home.

name: banette
pokedex_entry: BANETTE generates energy for laying strong curses by sticking pins into its own body. This POKéMON was originally a pitiful plush doll that was thrown away.

forms.name: banette-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: BANETTE generates energy for laying strong curses by sticking pins into its own body. This POKéMON was originally a pitiful plush doll that was thrown away.

name: duskull
pokedex_entry: DUSKULL can pass through any wall no matter how thick it may be. Once this POKéMON chooses a target, it will doggedly pursue the intended victim until the break of dawn.

name: dusclops
pokedex_entry: DUSCLOPS’s body is completely hollow - there is nothing at all inside. It is said that its body is like a black hole. This POKéMON will absorb anything into its body, but nothing will ever come back out.

name: tropius
pokedex_entry: The bunches of fruit around TROPIUS’s neck are very popular with children. This POKéMON loves fruit, and eats it continuously. Apparently, its love for fruit resulted in its own outgrowth of fruit.

name: chimecho
pokedex_entry: CHIMECHO makes its cries echo inside its hollow body. When this POKéMON becomes enraged, its cries result in ultrasonic waves that have the power to knock foes flying.

name: absol
pokedex_entry: Every time ABSOL appears before people, it is followed by a disaster such as an earthquake or a tidal wave. As a result, it came to be known as the disaster POKéMON.

forms.name: absol-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: Every time ABSOL appears before people, it is followed by a disaster such as an earthquake or a tidal wave. As a result, it came to be known as the disaster POKéMON.

name: wynaut
pokedex_entry: WYNAUT can always be seen with a big, happy smile on its face. Look at its tail to determine if it is angry. When angered, this POKéMON will be slapping the ground with its tail.

name: snorunt
pokedex_entry: SNORUNT live in regions with heavy snowfall. In seasons without snow, such as spring and summer, this POKéMON steals away to live quietly among stalactites and stalagmites deep in caverns.

name: glalie
pokedex_entry: GLALIE has a body made of rock, which it hardens with an armor of ice. This POKéMON has the ability to freeze moisture in the atmosphere into any shape it desires.

forms.name: glalie-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: GLALIE has a body made of rock, which it hardens with an armor of ice. This POKéMON has the ability to freeze moisture in the atmosphere into any shape it desires.

name: spheal
pokedex_entry: SPHEAL is much faster rolling than  walking to get around. When groups of this POKéMON eat, they all clap at once to show their pleasure. Because of this, their mealtimes are noisy.

name: sealeo
pokedex_entry: SEALEO has the habit of always juggling on the tip of its nose anything it sees for the first time. This POKéMON occasionally entertains itself by balancing and rolling a SPHEAL on its nose.

name: walrein
pokedex_entry: It swims through icy seas while shattering ice floes with its large tusks. It is protected by its thick blubber.

name: clamperl
pokedex_entry: CLAMPERL’s sturdy shell is not only good for protection - it is also used for clamping and catching prey. A fully grown CLAMPERL’s shell will be scored with nicks and scratches all over.

name: huntail
pokedex_entry: HUNTAIL’s presence went unnoticed by people for a long time because it lives at extreme depths in the sea. This POKéMON’s eyes can see clearly even in the murky dark depths of the ocean.

name: gorebyss
pokedex_entry: GOREBYSS lives in the southern seas at extreme depths. Its body is built to withstand the enormous pressure of water at incredible depths. Because of this, this POKéMON’s body is unharmed by ordinary attacks.

name: relicanth
pokedex_entry: RELICANTH is a POKéMON species that existed for a hundred million years without ever changing its form. This ancient POKéMON feeds on microscopic organisms with its toothless mouth.

name: luvdisc
pokedex_entry: LUVDISC live in shallow seas in the tropics. This heart-shaped POKéMON earned its name by swimming after loving couples it spotted in the ocean’s waves.

name: bagon
pokedex_entry: Dreaming of one day flying, it practices by leaping off cliffs every day.

name: shelgon
pokedex_entry: Inside SHELGON’s armor-like shell, cells are in the midst of transformation to create an entirely new body. This POKéMON’s shell is extremely heavy, making its movements sluggish.

name: salamence
pokedex_entry: SALAMENCE came about as a result of a strong, long-held dream of growing wings. It is said that this powerful desire triggered a sudden mutation in this POKéMON’s cells, causing it to sprout its magnificent wings.

forms.name: salamence-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: SALAMENCE came about as a result of a strong, long-held dream of growing wings. It is said that this powerful desire triggered a sudden mutation in this POKéMON’s cells, causing it to sprout its magnificent wings.

name: beldum
pokedex_entry: Instead of blood, a powerful magnetic force courses throughout BELDUM’s body. This POKéMON communicates with others by sending controlled pulses of magnetism.

name: metang
pokedex_entry: When two BELDUM fuse together, METANG is formed. The brains of the BELDUM are joined by a magnetic nervous system. By linking its brains magnetically, this POKéMON generates strong psychokinetic power.

name: metagross
pokedex_entry: METAGROSS has four brains in total. Combined, the four brains can breeze through difficult calculations faster than a supercomputer. This POKéMON can float in the air by tucking in its four legs.

forms.name: metagross-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: METAGROSS has four brains in total. Combined, the four brains can breeze through difficult calculations faster than a supercomputer. This POKéMON can float in the air by tucking in its four legs.

name: regirock
pokedex_entry: Its entire body is made of rock. If any part chips off in battle, it attaches rocks to repair itself.

name: regice
pokedex_entry: REGICE’s body was made during an ice age. The deep-frozen body can’t be melted, even by fire. This POKéMON controls frigid air of minus 328 degrees F.

name: registeel
pokedex_entry: REGISTEEL has a body that is harder than any kind of metal. Its body is apparently hollow. No one has any idea what this POKéMON eats.

name: latias
pokedex_entry: LATIAS is highly sensitive to the emotions of people. If it senses any hostility, this POKéMON ruffles the feathers all over its body and cries shrilly to intimidate the foe.

forms.name: latias-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: LATIAS is highly sensitive to the emotions of people. If it senses any hostility, this POKéMON ruffles the feathers all over its body and cries shrilly to intimidate the foe.

name: latios
pokedex_entry: LATIOS has the ability to make its foe see an image of what it has seen or imagines in its head. This POKéMON is intelligent and understands human speech.

forms.name: latios-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: LATIOS has the ability to make its foe see an image of what it has seen or imagines in its head. This POKéMON is intelligent and understands human speech.

name: kyogre
pokedex_entry: KYOGRE has the power to create massive rain clouds that cover the entire sky and bring about torrential downpours. This POKéMON saved people who were suffering from droughts.

forms.name: kyogre-primal
forms.pokedex_entry: KYOGRE has the power to create massive rain clouds that cover the entire sky and bring about torrential downpours. This POKéMON saved people who were suffering from droughts.

name: groudon
pokedex_entry: GROUDON has long been described in  mythology as the POKéMON that raised lands and expanded continents. This POKéMON took to sleep after a cataclysmic battle with KYOGRE.

forms.name: groudon-primal
forms.pokedex_entry: GROUDON has long been described in  mythology as the POKéMON that raised lands and expanded continents. This POKéMON took to sleep after a cataclysmic battle with KYOGRE.

name: rayquaza
pokedex_entry: RAYQUAZA lived for hundreds of millions of years in the earth’s ozone layer,  never descending to the ground. This POKéMON appears to feed on water and particles in the atmosphere.

forms.name: rayquaza-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: RAYQUAZA lived for hundreds of millions of years in the earth’s ozone layer,  never descending to the ground. This POKéMON appears to feed on water and particles in the atmosphere.

name: jirachi
pokedex_entry: A legend states that JIRACHI will make true any wish that is written on notes attached to its head when it awakens. If this POKéMON senses danger, it will fight without awakening.

name: deoxys-normal
pokedex_entry: The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in DEOXYS. The crystalline organ on this POKéMON’s chest appears to be its brain.

forms.name: deoxys-attack
forms.pokedex_entry: The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in DEOXYS. The crystalline organ on this POKéMON’s chest appears to be its brain.

forms.name: deoxys-defense
forms.pokedex_entry: The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in DEOXYS. The crystalline organ on this POKéMON’s chest appears to be its brain.

forms.name: deoxys-speed
forms.pokedex_entry: The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in DEOXYS. The crystalline organ on this POKéMON’s chest appears to be its brain.

name: turtwig
pokedex_entry: Made from soil, the shell on its back hardens when it drinks water. It lives along lakes.

name: grotle
pokedex_entry: It knows where pure water wells up. It carries fellow Pokémon there on its back.

name: torterra
pokedex_entry: Small Pokémon occasionally gather on its unmoving back to begin building their nests.

name: chimchar
pokedex_entry: It agilely scales sheer cliffs to live atop craggy mountains. Its fire is put out when it sleeps.

name: monferno
pokedex_entry: To intimidate attackers, it stretches the fire on its tail to make itself appear bigger.

name: infernape
pokedex_entry: It uses a special kind of martial arts involving all its limbs. Its fire never goes out.

name: piplup
pokedex_entry: Because it is very proud, it hates accepting food from people. Its thick down guards it from cold.

name: prinplup
pokedex_entry: It lives alone, away from others. Apparently, every one of them believes it is the most important.

name: empoleon
pokedex_entry: The three horns that extend from its beak attest to its power. The leader has the biggest horns.

name: starly
pokedex_entry: They flock in great numbers. Though small, they flap their wings with great power.

name: staravia
pokedex_entry: It flies around forests and fields in search of bug Pokémon. It stays within a huge flock.

name: staraptor
pokedex_entry: It has a savage nature. It will courageously challenge foes that are much larger.

name: bidoof
pokedex_entry: With nerves of steel, nothing can perturb it. It is more agile and active than it appears.

name: bibarel
pokedex_entry: It makes its nest by damming streams with bark and mud. It is known as an industrious worker.

name: kricketot
pokedex_entry: It shakes its head back to front, causing its antennae to hit each other and sound like a xylophone.

name: kricketune
pokedex_entry: It crosses its knifelike arms in front of its chest when it cries. It can compose melodies ad lib.

name: shinx
pokedex_entry: All of its fur dazzles if danger is sensed. It flees while the foe is momentarily blinded.

name: luxio
pokedex_entry: Its claws loose electricity with enough amperage to cause fainting. They live in small groups.

name: luxray
pokedex_entry: It has eyes that can see through anything. It spots and captures prey hiding behind objects.

name: budew
pokedex_entry: Over the winter, it closes its bud and endures the cold. In spring, the bud opens and releases pollen.

name: roserade
pokedex_entry: It attracts prey with a sweet aroma, then downs it with thorny whips hidden in its arms.

name: cranidos
pokedex_entry: It lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its skull is as hard as iron.

name: rampardos
pokedex_entry: Its powerful head butt has enough power to shatter even the most durable things upon impact.

name: shieldon
pokedex_entry: A Pokémon that lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its facial hide is extremely hard.

name: bastiodon
pokedex_entry: Any frontal attack is repulsed. It is a docile Pokémon that feeds on grass and berries.

name: burmy
pokedex_entry: To shelter itself from cold, wintry winds, it covers itself with a cloak made of twigs and leaves.

name: wormadam-plant
pokedex_entry: When BURMY evolved, its cloak became a part of this Pokémon’s body. The cloak is never shed.

forms.name: wormadam-sandy
forms.pokedex_entry: When BURMY evolved, its cloak became a part of this Pokémon’s body. The cloak is never shed.

forms.name: wormadam-trash
forms.pokedex_entry: When BURMY evolved, its cloak became a part of this Pokémon’s body. The cloak is never shed.

name: mothim
pokedex_entry: It loves the honey of flowers and steals honey collected by COMBEE.

name: combee
pokedex_entry: A Pokémon formed by three others. It busily carries sweet floral honey to VESPIQUEN.

name: vespiquen
pokedex_entry: Its abdomen is a honeycomb for grubs. It raises its grubs on honey collected by COMBEE.

name: pachirisu
pokedex_entry: It makes fur balls that crackle with static electricity. It stores them with berries in tree holes.

name: buizel
pokedex_entry: It has a flotation sac that is like an inflatable collar. It floats on water with its head out.

name: floatzel
pokedex_entry: It floats using its well-developed flotation sac. It assists in the rescues of drowning people.

name: cherubi
pokedex_entry: The small ball holds the nutrients needed for evolution. Apparently, it is very sweet and tasty.

name: cherrim
pokedex_entry: It blooms during times of strong sunlight. It tries to make up for everything it endured as a bud.

name: shellos
pokedex_entry: Its colors and shapes differ from region to region. In the Sinnoh region, two types are confirmed.

name: gastrodon
pokedex_entry: It has a pliable body without any bones. If any part of its body is torn off, it grows right back.

name: ambipom
pokedex_entry: To eat, it deftly shucks nuts with its two tails. It rarely uses its arms now.

name: drifloon
pokedex_entry: A Pokémon formed by the spirits of people and Pokémon. It loves damp, humid seasons.

name: drifblim
pokedex_entry: At dusk, swarms of them are carried aloft on winds. When noticed, they suddenly vanish.

name: buneary
pokedex_entry: It slams foes by sharply uncoiling its rolled ears. It stings enough to make a grown-up cry in pain.

name: lopunny
pokedex_entry: An extremely cautious Pokémon. It cloaks its body with its fluffy ear fur when it senses danger.

forms.name: lopunny-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: An extremely cautious Pokémon. It cloaks its body with its fluffy ear fur when it senses danger.

name: mismagius
pokedex_entry: Its cries sound like incantations. Those hearing it are tormented by headaches and hallucinations.

name: honchkrow
pokedex_entry: Becoming active at night, it is known to swarm with numerous MURKROW in tow.

name: glameow
pokedex_entry: It claws if displeased and purrs when affectionate. Its fickleness is very popular among some.

name: purugly
pokedex_entry: It is a brazen brute that barges its way into another Pokémon’s nest and claims it as its own.

name: chingling
pokedex_entry: It emits cries by agitating an orb at the back of its throat. It moves with flouncing hops.

name: stunky
pokedex_entry: It protects itself by spraying a noxious fluid from its rear. The stench lingers for 24 hours.

name: skuntank
pokedex_entry: It sprays a vile-smelling fluid from the tip of its tail to attack. Its range is over 160 feet.

name: bronzor
pokedex_entry: Implements shaped like it were discovered in ancient tombs. It is unknown if they are related.

name: bronzong
pokedex_entry: One caused a news sensation when it was dug up at a construction site after a 2,000-year sleep.

name: bonsly
pokedex_entry: It looks as if it is always crying. It is actually adjusting its body’s fluid levels by eliminating excess.

name: mime jr.
pokedex_entry: It habitually mimics foes. Once mimicked, the foe cannot take its eyes off this Pokémon.

name: happiny
pokedex_entry: It loves round white things. It carries an egg-shaped rock in imitation of CHANSEY.

name: chatot
pokedex_entry: It can learn and speak human words. If they gather, they all learn the same saying.

name: spiritomb
pokedex_entry: A Pokémon that was formed by 108 spirits. It is bound to a fissure in an odd keystone.

name: gible
pokedex_entry: It nests in small, horizontal holes in cave walls. It pounces to catch prey that stray too close.

name: gabite
pokedex_entry: There is a long-held belief that medicine made from its scales will heal even incurable illnesses.

name: garchomp
pokedex_entry: When it folds up its body and extends its wings, it looks like a jet plane. It flies at sonic speed.

forms.name: garchomp-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: When it folds up its body and extends its wings, it looks like a jet plane. It flies at sonic speed.

name: munchlax
pokedex_entry: It wolfs down its weight in food once a day, swallowing food whole with almost no chewing.

name: riolu
pokedex_entry: The aura that emanates from its body intensifies to alert others if it is afraid or sad.

name: lucario
pokedex_entry: It has the ability to sense the auras of all things. It understands human speech.

forms.name: lucario-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: It has the ability to sense the auras of all things. It understands human speech.

name: hippopotas
pokedex_entry: It lives in arid places. Instead of perspiration, it expels grainy sand from its body.

name: hippowdon
pokedex_entry: It blasts internally stored sand from ports on its body to create a towering twister for attack.

name: skorupi
pokedex_entry: It grips prey with its tail claws and injects poison. It tenaciously hangs on until the poison takes.

name: drapion
pokedex_entry: It has the power in its clawed arms to make scrap of a car. The tips of its claws release poison.

name: croagunk
pokedex_entry: Its cheeks hold poison sacs. It tries to catch foes off guard to jab them with toxic fingers.

name: toxicroak
pokedex_entry: Its knuckle claws secrete a toxin so vile that even a scratch could prove fatal.

name: carnivine
pokedex_entry: It attracts prey with its sweet- smelling saliva, then chomps down. It takes a whole day to eat prey.

name: finneon
pokedex_entry: After long exposure to sunlight, the patterns on its tail fins shine vividly when darkness arrives.

name: lumineon
pokedex_entry: It lives on the deep-sea floor. It attracts prey by flashing the patterns on its four tail fins.

name: mantyke
pokedex_entry: A friendly Pokémon that captures the subtle flows of seawater using its two antennae.

name: snover
pokedex_entry: It lives on snowy mountains. Having had little contact with humans, it is boldly inquisitive.

name: abomasnow
pokedex_entry: It whips up blizzards in mountains that are always buried in snow. It is the abominable snowman.

forms.name: abomasnow-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: It whips up blizzards in mountains that are always buried in snow. It is the abominable snowman.

name: weavile
pokedex_entry: They live in cold regions, forming groups of four or five that hunt prey with impressive coordination.

name: magnezone
pokedex_entry: It evolved from exposure to a special magnetic field. Three units generate magnetism.

name: lickilicky
pokedex_entry: It wraps things with its extensible tongue. Getting too close to it will leave you soaked with drool.

name: rhyperior
pokedex_entry: It puts rocks in holes in its palms and uses its muscles to shoot them. GEODUDE are shot at rare times.

name: tangrowth
pokedex_entry: It ensnares prey by extending arms made of vines. Losing arms to predators does not trouble it.

name: electivire
pokedex_entry: As its electric charge amplifies, blue sparks begin to crackle between its horns.

name: magmortar
pokedex_entry: It blasts fireballs of over 3,600 degrees F from the ends of its arms. It lives in volcanic craters.

name: togekiss
pokedex_entry: It will never appear where there is strife. Its sightings have become rare recently.

name: yanmega
pokedex_entry: By churning its wings, it creates shock waves that inflict critical internal injuries to foes.

name: leafeon
pokedex_entry: Just like a plant, it uses photosynthesis. As a result, it is always enveloped in clear air.

name: glaceon
pokedex_entry: As a protective technique, it can completely freeze its fur to make its hairs stand like needles.

name: gliscor
pokedex_entry: It observes prey while hanging inverted from branches. When the chance presents itself, it swoops!

name: mamoswine
pokedex_entry: Its impressive tusks are made of ice. The population thinned when it turned warm after the ice age.

name: porygon-z
pokedex_entry: Additional software was installed to make it a better Pokémon. It began acting oddly, however.

name: gallade
pokedex_entry: A master of courtesy and swordsmanship, it fights using extending swords on its elbows.

forms.name: gallade-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: A master of courtesy and swordsmanship, it fights using extending swords on its elbows.

name: probopass
pokedex_entry: It freely controls three small units called Mini-Noses using magnetic force.

name: dusknoir
pokedex_entry: The antenna on its head captures radio waves from the world of spirits that command it to take people there.

name: froslass
pokedex_entry: It freezes foes with an icy breath nearly -60 degrees F. What seems to be its body is actually hollow.

name: rotom
pokedex_entry: Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.

forms.name: rotom-heat
forms.pokedex_entry: Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.

forms.name: rotom-wash
forms.pokedex_entry: Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.

forms.name: rotom-frost
forms.pokedex_entry: Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.

forms.name: rotom-fan
forms.pokedex_entry: Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.

forms.name: rotom-mow
forms.pokedex_entry: Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.

name: uxie
pokedex_entry: Known as “The Being of Knowledge.” It is said that it can wipe out the memory of those who see its eyes.

name: mesprit
pokedex_entry: Known as “The Being of Emotion.” It taught humans the nobility of sorrow, pain, and joy.

name: azelf
pokedex_entry: Known as “The Being of Willpower.” It sleeps at the bottom of a lake to keep the world in balance.

name: dialga
pokedex_entry: It has the power to control time. It appears in Sinnoh-region myths as an ancient deity.

forms.name: dialga-origin
forms.pokedex_entry: It has the power to control time. It appears in Sinnoh-region myths as an ancient deity.

name: palkia
pokedex_entry: It has the ability to distort space. It is described as a deity in Sinnoh-region mythology.

forms.name: palkia-origin
forms.pokedex_entry: It has the ability to distort space. It is described as a deity in Sinnoh-region mythology.

name: heatran
pokedex_entry: It dwells in volcanic caves. It digs in with its cross-shaped feet to crawl on ceilings and walls.

name: regigigas
pokedex_entry: There is an enduring legend that states this Pokémon towed continents with ropes.

name: giratina-altered
pokedex_entry: A Pokémon that is said to live in a world on the reverse side of ours. It appears in an ancient cemetery.

forms.name: giratina-origin
forms.pokedex_entry: A Pokémon that is said to live in a world on the reverse side of ours. It appears in an ancient cemetery.

name: cresselia
pokedex_entry: Shiny particles are released from its wings like a veil. It is said to represent the crescent moon.

name: phione
pokedex_entry: It drifts in warm seas. It always returns to where it was born, no matter how far it may have drifted.

name: manaphy
pokedex_entry: Born on a cold seafloor, it will swim great distances to return to its birthplace.

name: darkrai
pokedex_entry: It can lull people to sleep and make them dream. It is active during nights of the new moon.

name: shaymin-land
pokedex_entry: It lives in flower patches and avoids detection by curling up to look like a flowering plant.

forms.name: shaymin-sky
forms.pokedex_entry: It lives in flower patches and avoids detection by curling up to look like a flowering plant.

name: arceus
pokedex_entry: It is described in mythology as the Pokémon that shaped the universe with its 1,000 arms.

name: victini
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon brings victory. It is said that Trainers with Victini always win, regardless of the type of encounter.

name: snivy
pokedex_entry: It is very intelligent and calm. Being exposed to lots of sunlight makes its movements swifter.

name: servine
pokedex_entry: It moves along the ground as if sliding. Its swift movements befuddle its foes, and it then attacks with a vine whip.

name: serperior
pokedex_entry: It can stop its opponents’ movements with just a glare. It takes in solar energy and boosts it internally.

name: tepig
pokedex_entry: It can deftly dodge its foe’s attacks while shooting fireballs from its nose. It roasts berries before it eats them.

name: pignite
pokedex_entry: When its internal fire flares up, its movements grow sharper and faster. When in trouble, it emits smoke.

name: emboar
pokedex_entry: It can throw a fire punch by setting its fists on fire with its fiery chin. It cares deeply about its friends.

name: oshawott
pokedex_entry: It fights using the scalchop on its stomach. In response to an attack, it retaliates immediately by slashing.

name: dewott
pokedex_entry: Strict training is how it learns its flowing double-scalchop technique.

name: samurott
pokedex_entry: One swing of the sword incorporated in its armor can fell an opponent. A simple glare from one of them quiets everybody.

forms.name: hisuian-samurott
forms.pokedex_entry: One swing of the sword incorporated in its armor can fell an opponent. A simple glare from one of them quiets everybody.

name: patrat
pokedex_entry: Using food stored in cheek pouches, they can keep watch for days. They use their tails to communicate with others.

name: watchog
pokedex_entry: When they see an enemy, their tails stand high, and they spit the seeds of berries stored in their cheek pouches.

name: lillipup
pokedex_entry: It faces strong opponents with great courage. But, when at a disadvantage in a fight, this intelligent Pokémon flees.

name: herdier
pokedex_entry: It has black, cape-like fur that is very hard and decreases the amount of damage it receives.

name: stoutland
pokedex_entry: It rescues people stranded by blizzards in the mountains. Its shaggy fur shields it from the cold.

name: purrloin
pokedex_entry: They steal from people for fun, but their victims can’t help but forgive them. Their deceptively cute act is perfect.

name: liepard
pokedex_entry: These Pokémon vanish and appear unexpectedly. Many Trainers are drawn to their beautiful form and fur.

name: pansage
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon dwells deep in the forest. Eating a leaf from its head whisks weariness away as if by magic.

name: simisage
pokedex_entry: Ill tempered, it fights by swinging its barbed tail around wildly. The leaf growing on its head is very bitter.

name: pansear
pokedex_entry: When it is angered, the temperature of its head tuft reaches 600° F. It uses its tuft to roast berries.

name: simisear
pokedex_entry: It loves sweets because they become energy for the fire burning inside its body.

name: panpour
pokedex_entry: The water stored inside the tuft on its head is full of nutrients. Plants that receive its water grow large.

name: simipour
pokedex_entry: The tuft on its head holds water. When the level runs low, it replenishes the tuft by siphoning up water with its tail.

name: munna
pokedex_entry: Munna always float in the air. People whose dreams are eaten by them forget what the dreams had been about.

name: musharna
pokedex_entry: The mist emanating from their foreheads is packed with the dreams of people and Pokémon.

name: pidove
pokedex_entry: Each follows its Trainer’s orders as best it can, but they sometimes fail to understand complicated commands.

name: tranquill
pokedex_entry: It can return to its Trainer’s location regardless of the distance separating them.

name: unfezant
pokedex_entry: Males swing their head plumage to threaten opponents. The females’ flying abilities surpass those of the males.

forms.name: unfezant-female
forms.pokedex_entry: Males swing their head plumage to threaten opponents. The females’ flying abilities surpass those of the males.

name: blitzle
pokedex_entry: When thunderclouds cover the sky, it will appear. It can catch lightning with its mane and store the electricity.

name: zebstrika
pokedex_entry: They have lightning-like movements. When Zebstrika run at full speed, the sound of thunder reverberates.

name: roggenrola
pokedex_entry: Its ear is hexagonal in shape. Compressed underground, its body is as hard as steel.

name: boldore
pokedex_entry: When it overflows with power, the orange crystal on its body glows. It looks for underground water in caves.

name: gigalith
pokedex_entry: Compressing the energy from its internal core lets it fire off an attack capable of blowing away a mountain.

name: woobat
pokedex_entry: Its habitat is dark forests and caves. It emits ultrasonic waves from its nose to learn about its surroundings.

name: swoobat
pokedex_entry: It emits sound waves of various frequencies from its nose, including some powerful enough to destroy rocks.

name: drilbur
pokedex_entry: It can dig through the ground at a speed of 30 mph. It could give a car running aboveground a good race.

name: excadrill
pokedex_entry: It can help in tunnel construction. Its drill has evolved into steel strong enough to bore through iron plates.

name: audino
pokedex_entry: It touches others with the feelers on its ears, using the sound of their heartbeats to tell how they are feeling.

forms.name: audino-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: It touches others with the feelers on its ears, using the sound of their heartbeats to tell how they are feeling.

name: timburr
pokedex_entry: It fights by swinging a piece of lumber around. It is close to evolving when it can handle the lumber without difficulty.

name: gurdurr
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon is so muscular and strongly built that even a group of wrestlers could not make it budge an inch.

name: conkeldurr
pokedex_entry: It is thought that Conkeldurr taught humans how to make concrete more than 2,000 years ago.

name: tympole
pokedex_entry: They warn others of danger by vibrating their cheeks to create a high-pitched sound.

name: palpitoad
