pokedex_entry: When they vibrate the bumps on their heads, they can make waves in water or earthquake-like vibrations on land.

name: seismitoad
pokedex_entry: They shoot paralyzing liquid from their head bumps. They use vibration to hurt their opponents.

name: throh
pokedex_entry: When it tightens its belt, it becomes stronger. Wild Throh use vines to weave their own belts.

name: sawk
pokedex_entry: The sound of Sawk punching boulders and trees can be heard all the way from the mountains where they train.

name: sewaddle
pokedex_entry: Leavanny dress it in clothes they made for it when it hatched. It hides its head in its hood while it is sleeping.

name: swadloon
pokedex_entry: Forests where Swadloon live have superb foliage because the nutrients they make from fallen leaves nourish the plant life.

name: leavanny
pokedex_entry: Upon finding a small Pokémon, it weaves clothing for it from leaves, using the cutters on its arms and sticky silk.

name: venipede
pokedex_entry: Its bite injects a potent poison, enough to paralyze large bird Pokémon that try to prey on it.

name: whirlipede
pokedex_entry: Protected by a hard shell, it spins its body like a wheel and crashes furiously into its enemies.

name: scolipede
pokedex_entry: With quick movements, it chases down its foes, attacking relentlessly with its horns until it prevails.

name: cottonee
pokedex_entry: When attacked, it escapes by shooting cotton from its body. The cotton serves as a decoy to distract the attacker.

name: whimsicott
pokedex_entry: Like the wind, it can slip through any gap, no matter how small. It leaves balls of white fluff behind.

name: petilil
pokedex_entry: The leaves on its head are very bitter. Eating one of these leaves is known to refresh a tired body.

name: lilligant
pokedex_entry: Even veteran Trainers face a challenge in getting its beautiful flower to bloom. This Pokémon is popular with celebrities.

forms.name: hisuian-lilligant
forms.pokedex_entry: Even veteran Trainers face a challenge in getting its beautiful flower to bloom. This Pokémon is popular with celebrities.

name: basculin
pokedex_entry: Red and blue Basculin get along so poorly, they’ll start fighting instantly. These Pokémon are very hostile.

forms.name: basculin-blue-striped
forms.pokedex_entry: Red and blue Basculin get along so poorly, they’ll start fighting instantly. These Pokémon are very hostile.

forms.name: basculin-white-striped
forms.pokedex_entry: Red and blue Basculin get along so poorly, they’ll start fighting instantly. These Pokémon are very hostile.

name: sandile
pokedex_entry: They live buried in the sands of the desert. The sun-warmed sands prevent their body temperature from dropping.

name: krokorok
pokedex_entry: They live in groups of a few individuals. Protective membranes shield their eyes from sandstorms.

name: krookodile
pokedex_entry: They never allow prey to escape. Their jaws are so powerful, they can crush the body of an automobile.

name: darumaka
pokedex_entry: When its internal fire is burning, it cannot calm down and it runs around. When the fire diminishes, it falls asleep.

forms.name: galarian-darumaka
forms.pokedex_entry: When its internal fire is burning, it cannot calm down and it runs around. When the fire diminishes, it falls asleep.

name: darmanitan
pokedex_entry: Its internal fire burns at 2,500° F, making enough power that it can destroy a dump truck with one punch.

forms.name: darmanitan-zen
forms.pokedex_entry: Its internal fire burns at 2,500° F, making enough power that it can destroy a dump truck with one punch.

forms.name: galarian-darmanitan
forms.pokedex_entry: Its internal fire burns at 2,500° F, making enough power that it can destroy a dump truck with one punch.

forms.name: galarian-darmanitan-zen
forms.pokedex_entry: Its internal fire burns at 2,500° F, making enough power that it can destroy a dump truck with one punch.

name: maractus
pokedex_entry: It uses an up-tempo song and dance to drive away the bird Pokémon that prey on its flower seeds.

name: dwebble
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon can easily melt holes in hard rocks with a liquid secreted from its mouth.

name: crustle
pokedex_entry: Competing for territory, Crustle fight viciously. The one whose boulder is broken is the loser of the battle.

name: scraggy
pokedex_entry: Its skin has a rubbery elasticity, so it can reduce damage by defensively pulling its skin up to its neck.

name: scrafty
pokedex_entry: Groups of them beat up anything that enters their territory. Each can spit acidic liquid from its mouth.

name: sigilyph
pokedex_entry: They never vary the route they fly, because their memories of guarding an ancient city remain steadfast.

name: yamask
pokedex_entry: Each of them carries a mask that used to be its face when it was human. Sometimes they look at it and cry.

forms.name: galarian-yamask
forms.pokedex_entry: Each of them carries a mask that used to be its face when it was human. Sometimes they look at it and cry.

name: cofagrigus
pokedex_entry: It has been said that they swallow those who get too close and turn them into mummies. They like to eat gold nuggets.

name: tirtouga
pokedex_entry: Restored from a fossil, this Pokémon can dive to depths beyond half a mile.

name: carracosta
pokedex_entry: They can live both in the ocean and on land. A slap from one of them is enough to open a hole in the bottom of a tanker.

name: archen
pokedex_entry: Said to be an ancestor of bird Pokémon, they were unable to fly and moved about by hopping from one branch to another.

name: archeops
pokedex_entry: They are intelligent and will cooperate to catch prey. From the ground, they use a running start to take flight.

name: trubbish
pokedex_entry: Inhaling the gas they belch will make you sleep for a week. They prefer unsanitary places.

name: garbodor
pokedex_entry: It clenches opponents with its left arm and finishes them off with foul-smelling poison gas belched from its mouth.

forms.name: garbodor-gmax
forms.pokedex_entry: It clenches opponents with its left arm and finishes them off with foul-smelling poison gas belched from its mouth.

name: zorua
pokedex_entry: It changes into the forms of others to surprise them. Apparently, it often transforms into a silent child.

forms.name: hisuian-zorua
forms.pokedex_entry: It changes into the forms of others to surprise them. Apparently, it often transforms into a silent child.

name: zoroark
pokedex_entry: Bonds between these Pokémon are very strong. It protects the safety of its pack by tricking its opponents.

forms.name: hisuian-zoroark
forms.pokedex_entry: Bonds between these Pokémon are very strong. It protects the safety of its pack by tricking its opponents.

name: minccino
pokedex_entry: They greet one another by rubbing each other with their tails, which are always kept well groomed and clean.

name: cinccino
pokedex_entry: Their white fur is coated in a special oil that makes it easy for them to deflect attacks.

name: gothita
pokedex_entry: Their ribbonlike feelers increase their psychic power. They are always staring at something.

name: gothorita
pokedex_entry: They use hypnosis to control people and Pokémon. Tales of Gothorita leading people astray are told in every corner.

name: gothitelle
pokedex_entry: Starry skies thousands of light-years away are visible in the space distorted by their intense psychic power.

name: solosis
pokedex_entry: They drive away attackers by unleashing psychic power. They can use telepathy to talk with others.

name: duosion
pokedex_entry: Since they have two divided brains, at times they suddenly try to take two different actions at once.

name: reuniclus
pokedex_entry: When Reuniclus shake hands, a network forms between their brains, increasing their psychic power.

name: ducklett
pokedex_entry: These bird Pokémon are excellent divers. They swim around in the water eating their favorite food--peat moss.

name: swanna
pokedex_entry: Swanna start to dance at dusk. The one dancing in the middle is the leader of the flock.

name: vanillite
pokedex_entry: The temperature of their breath is -58° F. They create snow crystals and make snow fall in the areas around them.

name: vanillish
pokedex_entry: Snowy mountains are this Pokémon’s habitat. During an ancient ice age, they moved to southern areas.

name: vanilluxe
pokedex_entry: Swallowing large amounts of water, they make snow clouds inside their bodies and attack their foes with violent blizzards.

name: deerling
pokedex_entry: The color and scent of their fur changes to match the mountain grass. When they sense hostility, they hide in the grass.

name: sawsbuck
pokedex_entry: They migrate according to the seasons. People can tell the season by looking at Sawsbuck’s horns.

name: emolga
pokedex_entry: The energy made in its cheeks’ electric pouches is stored inside its membrane and released while it is gliding.

name: karrablast
pokedex_entry: These mysterious Pokémon evolve when they receive electrical stimulation while they are in the same place as Shelmet.

name: escavalier
pokedex_entry: They fly around at high speed, striking with their pointed spears. Even when in trouble, they face opponents bravely.

name: foongus
pokedex_entry: It lures people in with its Poké Ball pattern, then releases poison spores. Why it resembles a Poké Ball is unknown.

name: amoonguss
pokedex_entry: It lures prey close by dancing and waving its arm caps, which resemble Poké Balls, in a swaying motion.

name: frillish
pokedex_entry: With its thin, veil-like arms wrapped around the body of its opponent, it sinks to the ocean floor.

name: jellicent
pokedex_entry: The fate of the ships and crew that wander into Jellicent’s habitat: all sunken, all lost, all vanished.

name: alomomola
pokedex_entry: The special membrane enveloping Alomomola has the ability to heal wounds.

name: joltik
pokedex_entry: Joltik that live in cities have learned a technique for sucking electricity from the outlets in houses.

name: galvantula
pokedex_entry: When attacked, they create an electric barrier by spitting out many electrically charged threads.

name: ferroseed
pokedex_entry: When threatened, it attacks by shooting a barrage of spikes, which gives it a chance to escape by rolling away.

name: ferrothorn
pokedex_entry: It fights by swinging around its three spiky feelers. A hit from these steel spikes can reduce a boulder to rubble.

name: klink
pokedex_entry: The two minigears that mesh together are predetermined. Each will rebound from other minigears without meshing.

name: klang
pokedex_entry: By changing the direction in which it rotates, it communicates its feelings to others. When angry, it rotates faster.

name: klinklang
pokedex_entry: The gear with the red core is rotated at high speed for a rapid energy charge.

name: tynamo
pokedex_entry: While one alone doesn’t have much power, a chain of many Tynamo can be as powerful as lightning.

name: eelektrik
pokedex_entry: They coil around foes and shock them with electricity-generating organs that seem simply to be circular patterns.

name: eelektross
pokedex_entry: They crawl out of the ocean using their arms. They will attack prey on shore and immediately drag it into the ocean.

name: elgyem
pokedex_entry: It uses its strong psychic power to squeeze its opponent’s brain, causing unendurable headaches.

name: beheeyem
pokedex_entry: It can manipulate an opponent’s memory. Apparently, it communicates by flashing its three different-colored fingers.

name: litwick
pokedex_entry: Litwick shines a light that absorbs the life energy of people and Pokémon, which becomes the fuel that it burns.

name: lampent
pokedex_entry: This ominous Pokémon is feared. Through cities it wanders, searching for the spirits of the fallen.

name: chandelure
pokedex_entry: It absorbs a spirit, which it then burns. By waving the flames on its arms, it puts its foes into a hypnotic trance.

name: axew
pokedex_entry: They use their tusks to crush the berries they eat. Repeated regrowth makes their tusks strong and sharp.

name: fraxure
pokedex_entry: Since a broken tusk will not grow back, they diligently sharpen their tusks on river rocks after they’ve been fighting.

name: haxorus
pokedex_entry: They are kind but can be relentless when defending territory. They challenge foes with tusks that can cut steel.

name: cubchoo
pokedex_entry: When it is not feeling well, its mucus gets watery and the power of its Ice-type moves decreases.

name: beartic
pokedex_entry: It can make its breath freeze at will. Very able in the water, it swims around in northern seas and catches prey.

name: cryogonal
pokedex_entry: When its body temperature goes up, it turns into steam and vanishes. When its temperature lowers, it returns to ice.

name: shelmet
pokedex_entry: When attacked, it defends itself by closing the lid of its shell. It can spit a sticky, poisonous liquid.

name: accelgor
pokedex_entry: When its body dries out, it weakens. So, to prevent dehydration, it wraps itself in many layers of thin membrane.

name: stunfisk
pokedex_entry: Its skin is very hard, so it is unhurt even if stepped on by sumo wrestlers. It smiles when transmitting electricity.

forms.name: galarian-stunfisk
forms.pokedex_entry: Its skin is very hard, so it is unhurt even if stepped on by sumo wrestlers. It smiles when transmitting electricity.

name: mienfoo
pokedex_entry: In fights, they dominate with onslaughts of flowing, continuous attacks. With their sharp claws, they cut enemies.

name: mienshao
pokedex_entry: It wields the fur on its arms like a whip. Its arm attacks come with such rapidity that they cannot even be seen.

name: druddigon
pokedex_entry: It warms its body by absorbing sunlight with its wings. When its body temperature falls, it can no longer move.

name: golett
pokedex_entry: The energy that burns inside it enables it to move, but no one has yet been able to identify this energy.

name: golurk
pokedex_entry: It flies across the sky at Mach speeds. Removing the seal on its chest makes its internal energy go out of control.

name: pawniard
pokedex_entry: Blades comprise this Pokémon’s entire body. If battling dulls the blades, it sharpens them on stones by the river.

name: bisharp
pokedex_entry: It leads a group of Pawniard. It battles to become the boss, but will be driven from the group if it loses.

name: bouffalant
pokedex_entry: Their fluffy fur absorbs damage, even if they strike foes with a fierce headbutt.

name: rufflet
pokedex_entry: They crush berries with their talons. They bravely stand up to any opponent, no matter how strong it is.

name: braviary
pokedex_entry: They fight for their friends without any thought about danger to themselves. One can carry a car while flying.

forms.name: hisuian-braviary
forms.pokedex_entry: They fight for their friends without any thought about danger to themselves. One can carry a car while flying.

name: vullaby
pokedex_entry: Their wings are too tiny to allow them to fly. They guard their posteriors with bones that were gathered by Mandibuzz.

name: mandibuzz
pokedex_entry: It makes a nest out of bones it finds. It grabs weakened prey in its talons and hauls it to its nest of bones.

name: heatmor
pokedex_entry: It breathes through a hole in its tail while it burns with an internal fire. Durant is its prey.

name: durant
pokedex_entry: They attack in groups, covering themselves in steel armor to protect themselves from Heatmor.

name: deino
pokedex_entry: It tends to bite everything, and it is not a picky eater. Approaching it carelessly is dangerous.

name: zweilous
pokedex_entry: After it has eaten up all the food in its territory, it moves to another area. Its two heads do not get along.

name: hydreigon
pokedex_entry: This brutal Pokémon travels the skies on its six wings. Anything that moves seems like a foe to it, triggering its attack.

name: larvesta
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon was believed to have been born from the sun. When it evolves, its entire body is engulfed in flames.

name: volcarona
pokedex_entry: When volcanic ash darkened the atmosphere, it is said that Volcarona’s fire provided a replacement for the sun.

name: cobalion
pokedex_entry: This legendary Pokémon battled against humans to protect Pokémon. Its personality is calm and composed.

name: terrakion
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon came to the defense of Pokémon that had lost their homes in a war among humans.

name: virizion
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon fought humans in order to protect its friends. Legends about it continue to be passed down.

name: tornadus-incarnate
pokedex_entry: The lower half of its body is wrapped in a cloud of energy. It zooms through the sky at 200 mph.

forms.name: tornadus-therian
forms.pokedex_entry: The lower half of its body is wrapped in a cloud of energy. It zooms through the sky at 200 mph.

name: thundurus-incarnate
pokedex_entry: Countless charred remains mar the landscape of places through which Thundurus has passed.

forms.name: thundurus-therian
forms.pokedex_entry: Countless charred remains mar the landscape of places through which Thundurus has passed.

name: reshiram
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon appears in legends. It sends flames into the air from its tail, burning up everything around it.

name: zekrom
pokedex_entry: Concealing itself in lightning clouds, it flies throughout the Unova region. It creates electricity in its tail.

name: landorus-incarnate
pokedex_entry: Lands visited by Landorus grant such bountiful crops that it has been hailed as “The Guardian of the Fields.”

forms.name: landorus-therian
forms.pokedex_entry: Lands visited by Landorus grant such bountiful crops that it has been hailed as “The Guardian of the Fields.”

name: kyurem
pokedex_entry: It generates a powerful, freezing energy inside itself, but its body became frozen when the energy leaked out.

forms.name: kyurem-black
forms.pokedex_entry: It generates a powerful, freezing energy inside itself, but its body became frozen when the energy leaked out.

forms.name: kyurem-white
forms.pokedex_entry: It generates a powerful, freezing energy inside itself, but its body became frozen when the energy leaked out.

name: keldeo-ordinary
pokedex_entry: By blasting water from its hooves, it can glide across water. It excels at using leg moves while battling.

forms.name: keldeo-resolute
forms.pokedex_entry: By blasting water from its hooves, it can glide across water. It excels at using leg moves while battling.

name: meloetta-aria
pokedex_entry: Its melodies are sung with a special vocalization method that can control the feelings of those who hear it.

forms.name: meloetta-pirouette
forms.pokedex_entry: Its melodies are sung with a special vocalization method that can control the feelings of those who hear it.

name: genesect
pokedex_entry: Over 300 million years ago, it was feared as the strongest of hunters. It has been modified by Team Plasma.

name: chespin
pokedex_entry: The quills on its head are usually soft. When it flexes them, the points become so hard and sharp that they can pierce rock.

name: quilladin
pokedex_entry: It relies on its sturdy shell to deflect predators’ attacks. It counterattacks with its sharp quills.

name: chesnaught
pokedex_entry: Its Tackle is forceful enough to flip a 50-ton tank. It shields its allies from danger with its own body.

name: fennekin
pokedex_entry: Eating a twig fills it with energy, and its roomy ears give vent to air hotter than 390 degrees Fahrenheit.

name: braixen
pokedex_entry: It has a twig stuck in its tail. With friction from its tail fur, it sets the twig on fire and launches into battle.

name: delphox
pokedex_entry: It gazes into the flame at the tip of its branch to achieve a focused state, which allows it to see into the future.

name: froakie
pokedex_entry: It secretes flexible bubbles from its chest and back. The bubbles reduce the damage it would otherwise take when attacked.

name: frogadier
pokedex_entry: It can throw bubble-covered pebbles with precise control, hitting empty cans up to a hundred feet away.

name: greninja
pokedex_entry: It creates throwing stars out of compressed water. When it spins them and throws them at high speed, these stars can split metal in two.

forms.name: greninja-battle-bond
forms.pokedex_entry: It creates throwing stars out of compressed water. When it spins them and throws them at high speed, these stars can split metal in two.

forms.name: greninja-ash
forms.pokedex_entry: It creates throwing stars out of compressed water. When it spins them and throws them at high speed, these stars can split metal in two.

name: bunnelby
pokedex_entry: They use their large ears to dig burrows. They will dig the whole night through.

name: diggersby
pokedex_entry: With their powerful ears, they can heft boulders of a ton or more with ease. They can be a big help at construction sites.

name: fletchling
pokedex_entry: These friendly Pokémon send signals to one another with beautiful chirps and tail-feather movements.

name: fletchinder
pokedex_entry: From its beak, it expels embers that set the tall grass on fire. Then it pounces on the bewildered prey that pop out of the grass.

name: talonflame
pokedex_entry: In the fever of an exciting battle, it showers embers from the gaps between its feathers and takes to the air.

name: scatterbug
pokedex_entry: When under attack from bird Pokémon, it spews a poisonous black powder that causes paralysis on contact.

name: spewpa
pokedex_entry: It lives hidden within thicket shadows. When predators attack, it quickly bristles the fur covering its body in an effort to threaten them.

name: vivillon
pokedex_entry: Vivillon with many different patterns are found all over the world. These patterns are affected by the climate of their habitat.

name: litleo
pokedex_entry: The stronger the opponent it faces, the more heat surges from its mane and the more power flows through its body.

name: pyroar
pokedex_entry: The male with the largest mane of fire is the leader of the pride.

name: flabebe
pokedex_entry: It draws out and controls the hidden power of flowers. The flower Flabébé holds is most likely part of its body.

name: floette
pokedex_entry: It flutters around fields of flowers and cares for flowers that are starting to wilt. It draws out the hidden power of flowers to battle.

forms.name: floette-eternal
forms.pokedex_entry: It flutters around fields of flowers and cares for flowers that are starting to wilt. It draws out the hidden power of flowers to battle.

name: florges
pokedex_entry: It claims exquisite flower gardens as its territory, and it obtains power from basking in the energy emitted by flowering plants.

name: skiddo
pokedex_entry: Thought to be one of the first Pokémon to live in harmony with humans, it has a placid disposition.

name: gogoat
pokedex_entry: It can tell how its Trainer is feeling by subtle shifts in the grip on its horns. This empathic sense lets them run as if one being.

name: pancham
pokedex_entry: It does its best to be taken seriously by its enemies, but its glare is not sufficiently intimidating. Chewing on a leaf is its trademark.

name: pangoro
pokedex_entry: Although it possesses a violent temperament, it won’t put up with bullying. It uses the leaf in its mouth to sense the movements of its enemies.

name: furfrou
pokedex_entry: Trimming its fluffy fur not only makes it more elegant but also increases the swiftness of its movements.

name: espurr
pokedex_entry: The organ that emits its intense psychic power is sheltered by its ears to keep power from leaking out.

name: meowstic
pokedex_entry: When in danger, it raises its ears and releases enough psychic power to grind a 10-ton truck into dust.

forms.name: meowstic-female
forms.pokedex_entry: When in danger, it raises its ears and releases enough psychic power to grind a 10-ton truck into dust.

name: honedge
pokedex_entry: Apparently this Pokémon is born when a departed spirit inhabits a sword. It attaches itself to people and drinks their life force.

name: doublade
pokedex_entry: When Honedge evolves, it divides into two swords, which cooperate via telepathy to coordinate attacks and slash their enemies to ribbons.

name: aegislash-shield
pokedex_entry: Generations of kings were attended by these Pokémon, which used their spectral power to manipulate and control people and Pokémon.

forms.name: aegislash-blade
forms.pokedex_entry: Generations of kings were attended by these Pokémon, which used their spectral power to manipulate and control people and Pokémon.

name: spritzee
pokedex_entry: It emits a scent that enraptures those who smell it. This fragrance changes depending on what it has eaten.

name: aromatisse
pokedex_entry: It devises various scents, pleasant and unpleasant, and emits scents that its enemies dislike in order to gain an edge in battle.

name: swirlix
pokedex_entry: To entangle its opponents in battle, it extrudes white threads as sweet and sticky as cotton candy.

name: slurpuff
pokedex_entry: It can distinguish the faintest of scents. It puts its sensitive sense of smell to use by helping pastry chefs in their work.

name: inkay
pokedex_entry: Opponents who stare at the flashing of the light-emitting spots on its body become dazed and lose their will to fight.

name: malamar
pokedex_entry: It wields the most compelling hypnotic powers of any Pokémon, and it forces others to do whatever it wants.

name: binacle
pokedex_entry: Two Binacle live together on one rock. When they fight, one of them will move to a different rock.

name: barbaracle
pokedex_entry: When they evolve, two Binacle multiply into seven. They fight with the power of seven Binacle.

name: skrelp
pokedex_entry: Camouflaged as rotten kelp, they spray liquid poison on prey that approaches unawares and then finish it off.

name: dragalge
pokedex_entry: Their poison is strong enough to eat through the hull of a tanker, and they spit it indiscriminately at anything that enters their territory.

name: clauncher
pokedex_entry: They knock down flying prey by firing compressed water from their massive claws like shooting a pistol.

name: clawitzer
pokedex_entry: Their enormous claws launch cannonballs of water powerful enough to pierce tanker hulls.

name: helioptile
pokedex_entry: They make their home in deserts. They can generate their energy from basking in the sun, so eating food is not a requirement.

name: heliolisk
pokedex_entry: They flare their frills and generate energy. A single Heliolisk can generate sufficient electricity to power a skyscraper.

name: tyrunt
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon was restored from a fossil. If something happens that it doesn’t like, it throws a tantrum and runs wild.

name: tyrantrum
pokedex_entry: Thanks to its gargantuan jaws, which could shred thick metal plates as if they were paper, it was invincible in the ancient world it once inhabited.

name: amaura
pokedex_entry: This ancient Pokémon was restored from part of its body that had been frozen in ice for over 100 million years.

name: aurorus
pokedex_entry: The diamond-shaped crystals on its body expel air as cold as -240 degrees Fahrenheit, surrounding its enemies and encasing them in ice.

name: sylveon
pokedex_entry: It sends a soothing aura from its ribbonlike feelers to calm fights.

name: hawlucha
pokedex_entry: Although its body is small, its proficient fighting skills enable it to keep up with big bruisers like Machamp and Hariyama.

name: dedenne
pokedex_entry: Its whiskers serve as antennas. By sending and receiving electrical waves, it can communicate with others over vast distances.

name: carbink
pokedex_entry: Born from the temperatures and pressures deep underground, it fires beams from the stone in its head.

name: goomy
pokedex_entry: The weakest Dragon-type Pokémon, it lives in damp, shady places, so its body doesn’t dry out.

name: sliggoo
pokedex_entry: It drives away opponents by excreting a sticky liquid that can dissolve anything. Its eyes devolved, so it can’t see anything.

forms.name: hisuian-sliggoo
forms.pokedex_entry: It drives away opponents by excreting a sticky liquid that can dissolve anything. Its eyes devolved, so it can’t see anything.

name: goodra
pokedex_entry: This very friendly Dragon-type Pokémon will hug its beloved Trainer, leaving that Trainer covered in sticky slime.

forms.name: hisuian-goodra
forms.pokedex_entry: This very friendly Dragon-type Pokémon will hug its beloved Trainer, leaving that Trainer covered in sticky slime.

name: klefki
pokedex_entry: These key collectors threaten any attackers by fiercely jingling their keys at them.

name: phantump
pokedex_entry: These Pokémon are created when spirits possess rotten tree stumps. They prefer to live in abandoned forests.

name: trevenant
pokedex_entry: It can control trees at will. It will trap people who harm the forest, so they can never leave.

name: pumpkaboo-average
pokedex_entry: The pumpkin body is inhabited by a spirit trapped in this world. As the sun sets, it becomes restless and active.

forms.name: pumpkaboo-small
forms.pokedex_entry: The pumpkin body is inhabited by a spirit trapped in this world. As the sun sets, it becomes restless and active.

forms.name: pumpkaboo-large
forms.pokedex_entry: The pumpkin body is inhabited by a spirit trapped in this world. As the sun sets, it becomes restless and active.

forms.name: pumpkaboo-super
forms.pokedex_entry: The pumpkin body is inhabited by a spirit trapped in this world. As the sun sets, it becomes restless and active.

name: gourgeist-average
pokedex_entry: Singing in eerie voices, they wander town streets on the night of the new moon. Anyone who hears their song is cursed.

forms.name: gourgeist-small
forms.pokedex_entry: Singing in eerie voices, they wander town streets on the night of the new moon. Anyone who hears their song is cursed.

forms.name: gourgeist-large
forms.pokedex_entry: Singing in eerie voices, they wander town streets on the night of the new moon. Anyone who hears their song is cursed.

forms.name: gourgeist-super
forms.pokedex_entry: Singing in eerie voices, they wander town streets on the night of the new moon. Anyone who hears their song is cursed.

name: bergmite
pokedex_entry: It blocks opponents’ attacks with the ice that shields its body. It uses cold air to repair any cracks with new ice.

name: avalugg
pokedex_entry: Its ice-covered body is as hard as steel. Its cumbersome frame crushes anything that stands in its way.

forms.name: hisuian-avalugg
forms.pokedex_entry: Its ice-covered body is as hard as steel. Its cumbersome frame crushes anything that stands in its way.

name: noibat
pokedex_entry: They live in pitch-black caves. Their enormous ears can emit ultrasonic waves of 200,000 hertz.

name: noivern
pokedex_entry: They fly around on moonless nights and attack careless prey. Nothing can beat them in a battle in the dark.

name: xerneas
pokedex_entry: Legends say it can share eternal life. It slept for a thousand years in the form of a tree before its revival.

name: yveltal
pokedex_entry: When this legendary Pokémon’s wings and tail feathers spread wide and glow red, it absorbs the life force of living creatures.

name: zygarde
pokedex_entry: When the Kalos region’s ecosystem falls into disarray, it appears and reveals its secret power.

forms.name: zygarde-10%
forms.pokedex_entry: When the Kalos region’s ecosystem falls into disarray, it appears and reveals its secret power.

forms.name: zygarde-complete
forms.pokedex_entry: When the Kalos region’s ecosystem falls into disarray, it appears and reveals its secret power.

forms.name: 10%-power-construct
forms.pokedex_entry: When the Kalos region’s ecosystem falls into disarray, it appears and reveals its secret power.

forms.name: 50%-power-construct
forms.pokedex_entry: When the Kalos region’s ecosystem falls into disarray, it appears and reveals its secret power.

name: diancie
pokedex_entry: A sudden transformation of Carbink, its pink, glimmering body is said to be the loveliest sight in the whole world.

forms.name: diancie-mega
forms.pokedex_entry: A sudden transformation of Carbink, its pink, glimmering body is said to be the loveliest sight in the whole world.

name: hoopa
pokedex_entry: This troublemaker sends anything and everything to faraway places using its loop, which can warp space.

forms.name: hoopa-unbound
forms.pokedex_entry: This troublemaker sends anything and everything to faraway places using its loop, which can warp space.

name: volcanion
pokedex_entry: It lets out billows of steam and disappears into the dense fog. It’s said to live in mountains where humans do not tread.

name: rowlet
pokedex_entry: This wary Pokémon uses photosynthesis to store up energy during the day, while becoming active at night.

name: dartrix
pokedex_entry: A bit of a dandy, it spends its free time preening its wings. Its preoccupation with any dirt on its plumage can leave it unable to battle.

name: decidueye
pokedex_entry: It fires arrow quills from its wings with such precision, they can pierce a pebble at distances over a hundred yards.

forms.name: hisuian-decidueye
forms.pokedex_entry: It fires arrow quills from its wings with such precision, they can pierce a pebble at distances over a hundred yards.

name: litten
pokedex_entry: While grooming itself, it builds up fur inside its stomach. It sets the fur alight and spews fiery attacks, which change based on how it coughs.

name: torracat
pokedex_entry: At its throat, it bears a bell of fire. The bell rings brightly whenever this Pokémon spits fire.

name: incineroar
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon has a violent, selfish disposition. If it’s not in the mood to listen, it will ignore its Trainer’s orders with complete nonchalance.

name: popplio
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon snorts body fluids from its nose, blowing balloons to smash into its foes. It’s famous for being a hard worker.

name: brionne
pokedex_entry: A skillful dancer, it creates a sequence of water balloons as it dances, and briskly bombards its enemies.

name: primarina
pokedex_entry: It controls its water balloons with song. The melody is learned from others of its kind and is passed down from one generation to the next.

name: pikipek
pokedex_entry: It can peck at a rate of 16 times a second to drill holes in trees. It uses the holes for food storage and for nesting.

name: trumbeak
pokedex_entry: It eats berries and stores their seeds in its beak. When it encounters enemies or prey, it fires off all the seeds in a burst.

name: toucannon
pokedex_entry: When it battles, its beak heats up. The temperature can easily exceed 212 degrees Fahrenheit, causing severe burns when it hits.

name: yungoos
pokedex_entry: With its sharp fangs, it will bite anything. It did not originally live in Alola but was imported from another region.

name: gumshoos
pokedex_entry: When it finds a trace of its prey, it patiently stakes out the location...but it’s always snoozing by nightfall.

forms.name: gumshoos-totem
forms.pokedex_entry: When it finds a trace of its prey, it patiently stakes out the location...but it’s always snoozing by nightfall.

name: grubbin
pokedex_entry: Its strong jaw enables it to scrape trees and slurp out the sap. It normally lives underground.

name: charjabug
pokedex_entry: Its body is capable of storing electricity. On camping trips, people are grateful to have one around.

name: vikavolt
pokedex_entry: It zips around, on sharp lookout for an opening. It concentrates electrical energy within its large jaws and uses it to zap its enemies.

forms.name: vikavolt-totem
forms.pokedex_entry: It zips around, on sharp lookout for an opening. It concentrates electrical energy within its large jaws and uses it to zap its enemies.

name: crabrawler
pokedex_entry: While guarding its weak points with its pincers, it looks for an opening and unleashes punches. When it loses, it foams at the mouth and faints.

name: crabominable
pokedex_entry: It aimed for the top but got lost and ended up on a snowy mountain. Being forced to endure the cold, this Pokémon evolved and grew fur.

name: oricorio-baile
pokedex_entry: It beats its wings together to create fire. As it moves in the steps of its beautiful dance, it bathes opponents in intense flames.

forms.name: oricorio-pom-pom
forms.pokedex_entry: It beats its wings together to create fire. As it moves in the steps of its beautiful dance, it bathes opponents in intense flames.

forms.name: oricorio-pau
forms.pokedex_entry: It beats its wings together to create fire. As it moves in the steps of its beautiful dance, it bathes opponents in intense flames.

forms.name: oricorio-sensu
forms.pokedex_entry: It beats its wings together to create fire. As it moves in the steps of its beautiful dance, it bathes opponents in intense flames.

name: cutiefly
pokedex_entry: It feeds on the nectar and pollen of flowers. Because it’s able to sense auras, it can identify which flowers are about to bloom.

name: ribombee
pokedex_entry: It rolls up pollen into puffs. It makes many different varieties, some used as food and others used in battle.

forms.name: ribombee-totem
forms.pokedex_entry: It rolls up pollen into puffs. It makes many different varieties, some used as food and others used in battle.

name: rockruff
pokedex_entry: It’s considered to be a good Pokémon for beginners because of its friendliness, but its disposition grows rougher as it grows up.

forms.name: rockruff-own-tempo
forms.pokedex_entry: It’s considered to be a good Pokémon for beginners because of its friendliness, but its disposition grows rougher as it grows up.

name: lycanroc-midday
pokedex_entry: Its quick movements confuse its enemies. Well equipped with claws and fangs, it also uses the sharp rocks in its mane as weapons.

forms.name: lycanroc-midnight
forms.pokedex_entry: Its quick movements confuse its enemies. Well equipped with claws and fangs, it also uses the sharp rocks in its mane as weapons.

forms.name: lycanroc-dusk
forms.pokedex_entry: Its quick movements confuse its enemies. Well equipped with claws and fangs, it also uses the sharp rocks in its mane as weapons.

name: wishiwashi-solo
pokedex_entry: When it’s in trouble, its eyes moisten and begin to shine. The shining light attracts its comrades, and they stand together against their enemies.

forms.name: wishiwashi-school
forms.pokedex_entry: When it’s in trouble, its eyes moisten and begin to shine. The shining light attracts its comrades, and they stand together against their enemies.

name: mareanie
pokedex_entry: It plunges the poison spike on its head into its prey. When the prey has weakened, Mareanie deals the finishing blow with its 10 tentacles.

name: toxapex
pokedex_entry: Toxapex crawls along the ocean floor on its 12 legs. It leaves a trail of Corsola bits scattered in its wake.

name: mudbray
pokedex_entry: The mud stuck to Mudbray’s hooves enhances its grip and its powerful running gait.

name: mudsdale
pokedex_entry: It spits a mud that provides resistance to both wind and rain, so the walls of old houses were often coated with it.

name: dewpider
pokedex_entry: It crawls onto the land in search of food. Its water bubble allows it to breathe and protects its soft head.

name: araquanid
pokedex_entry: It delivers headbutts with the water bubble on its head. Small Pokémon get sucked into the bubble, where they drown.

forms.name: araquanid-totem
forms.pokedex_entry: It delivers headbutts with the water bubble on its head. Small Pokémon get sucked into the bubble, where they drown.

name: fomantis
pokedex_entry: During the day, it sleeps and soaks up light. When night falls, it walks around looking for a safer place to sleep.

name: lurantis
pokedex_entry: It requires a lot of effort to maintain Lurantis’s vivid coloring, but some collectors enjoy this work and treat it as their hobby.

forms.name: lurantis-totem
forms.pokedex_entry: It requires a lot of effort to maintain Lurantis’s vivid coloring, but some collectors enjoy this work and treat it as their hobby.

name: morelull
pokedex_entry: It scatters spores that flicker and glow. Anyone seeing these lights falls into a deep slumber.

name: shiinotic
pokedex_entry: Forests where Shiinotic live are treacherous to enter at night. People confused by its strange lights can never find their way home again.

name: salandit
pokedex_entry: It burns its bodily fluids to create a poisonous gas. When its enemies become disoriented from inhaling the gas, it attacks them.

name: salazzle
pokedex_entry: For some reason, only females have been found. It creates a reverse harem of male Salandit that it lives with.

forms.name: salazzle-totem
forms.pokedex_entry: For some reason, only females have been found. It creates a reverse harem of male Salandit that it lives with.

name: stufful
pokedex_entry: Despite its adorable appearance, when it gets angry and flails about, its arms and legs could knock a pro wrestler sprawling.

name: bewear
pokedex_entry: This immensely dangerous Pokémon possesses overwhelming physical strength. Its habitat is generally off-limits.

name: bounsweet
pokedex_entry: A delectable aroma pours from its body. They are often swallowed whole by Toucannon lured by that wafting deliciousness.

name: steenee
pokedex_entry: The sepals on its head developed to protect its body. These are quite hard, so even if pecked by bird Pokémon, this Pokémon is totally fine.

name: tsareena
pokedex_entry: Its long, striking legs aren’t just for show but to be used to kick with skill. In victory, it shows off by kicking the defeated, laughing boisterously.

name: comfey
pokedex_entry: It attaches flowers to its highly nutritious vine. This revitalizes the flowers, and they give off an aromatic scent.

name: oranguru
pokedex_entry: Known for its extreme intelligence, this Pokémon will look down on inexperienced Trainers, so it’s best suited to veteran Trainers.

name: passimian
pokedex_entry: They form groups of roughly 20 individuals. Their mutual bond is remarkable—they will never let down a comrade.

name: wimpod
pokedex_entry: This Pokémon is a coward. As it desperately dashes off, the flailing of its many legs leaves a sparkling clean path in its wake.

name: golisopod
pokedex_entry: With a flashing slash of its giant sharp claws, it cleaves seawater—or even air—right in two.

name: sandygast
pokedex_entry: Born from a sand mound playfully built by a child, this Pokémon embodies the grudges of the departed.

name: palossand
pokedex_entry: Possessed people controlled by this Pokémon transformed its sand mound into a castle. As it evolved, its power to curse grew ever stronger.

name: pyukumuku
pokedex_entry: It’s covered in a slime that keeps its skin moist, allowing it to stay on land for days without drying up.

name: type-null
pokedex_entry: The heavy control mask it wears suppresses its intrinsic capabilities. This Pokémon has some hidden special power.

name: silvally
pokedex_entry: Its trust in its partner is what awakens it. This Pokémon is capable of changing its type, a flexibility that is well displayed in battle.

name: minior-red-meteor
pokedex_entry: Originally making its home in the ozone layer, it hurtles to the ground when the shell enclosing its body grows too heavy.

forms.name: minior-orange-meteor
forms.pokedex_entry: Originally making its home in the ozone layer, it hurtles to the ground when the shell enclosing its body grows too heavy.
